orter sans \u00eatre d\u00e9tenue comme une criminelle. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Cardinal","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/54861174"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:44:10Z","content":"There is no legal reason to hold Justine in Cuba. Please let her find some peace by coming home to attend her son's funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jo-Anne Cripps","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78868201"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:00:28Z","content":"Detaining someone for a reason like this is criminal","like_count":0,"author_name":"Aidan Tompkins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17201852"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:38:36Z","content":"Canad has to start helping their citizens.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Daniel Lacoste","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45243134"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:20:47Z","content":"As a mother I cannot imagine what this family is going through. Losing a child would probably be the most difficult thing but not being able to say goodbye... I can't even imagine how you would be able to move on. It is completely disgusting that there are people out there that would hold her hostage while her son is being buried so many miles away. I will never take my family there again.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christina Jaimungal","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78885674"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:29:51Z","content":"Is our country not helping her & if yes or no why is this so difficult it's important to know","like_count":0,"author_name":"nelson labelle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26797320"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T02:23:42Z","content":"Have some humanity people! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah Kay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78798201"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:58:24Z","content":"It's heartless to keep her from burying her little boy. The  fact that people should have to sign such a petition is pathetic. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"jennifer rankin","author_url":"http://a