 many ways.  This mother deserves to be allowed to say goodbye to her beloved child in the appropriate way at his funeral. Her emotional scars from this tragic incident will be longlasting already, and it is unconscionable that both the Cuban and Canadian governments are stonewalling and deliberating delaying her release without legitimate reason as far as the public is aware.  Please let this mother return home urgently so that she may lay her child to rest","like_count":0,"author_name":"Eni Keszthelyi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77715199"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:11:56Z","content":"I could never imagine that happening to me and not being able to put my child to rest. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"ANGELA WHALEY","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78915252"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:18:01Z","content":"This was such a tragic accident.  I am sure devastated doesn't even begin to describe how this mother is feeling.  I understand that the Cuban police need to investigate this accident but it happened over a month ago, what is taking so long??  She deserves to be at her sons funeral and if she needs to return to Cuba after that then so be it.  The Cuban government needs to have some compassion.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Natalie Payne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/55848780"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:24:02Z","content":"Because it isn't right that this Mother can't attend her own child's funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maria Correia","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43703964"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:38:23Z","content":"I am a mother and cannot even imagine being in this position.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bobbi Lee","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69263405"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:40:29Z","content":"My daughter was almost hit by a vehilce in Cuba while driving a scooter.  This story could be about us.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathaleen Strong","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65446307"