 a mother, I can't imagine the heart ache! If I was in this situation I would want the support! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"paula alvear","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78876243"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:22:16Z","content":"She has been through enough and should be with the people who love her.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathryn Ballett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78788099"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:44:48Z","content":"I think a lot of citizens don't understand that though they were told this is 'their' country (Canada), it is 'not' -- it is the Canadian 'elites' country.  A very hard awakening to that fact here, I am sure, and I feel for you deeply.  Message to the rest of us:  don't travel abroad, and at election time, choose a party that is NOT mainstream, to vote for (the mainstream ones all support the elites including the NDP).","like_count":0,"author_name":"Greg Hood","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59524156"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:49:52Z","content":"This unfortunate and tragic accident could happen to anyone, at any time. Some sympathy & humanity should be shown by the Cuban authorities in allowing this mother to begin the grieving process for her son, by attending his funeral. Show some compassion, please!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shelagh Bruhn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65062781"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:52:49Z","content":"I think that the mom and her actual situation is critical and our gov help is necessary","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sofiane boufas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35277594"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T03:28:45Z","content":"No mother should ever miss her childs funeral when the childs death was a true accident.  Universal law of the heart on matters like this should always take priority of mans law!  Cuba should be ashamed of this!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sherri Kejick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/64076395"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:01:13Z