at is wrong with our government ?   Get this women home so she can have her last good bye with her son . No one should have to go through this emotional pain alone in another country. Step up Canada !","like_count":0,"author_name":"Natasha Lowe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58849376"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:47:13Z","content":"An accident abroad is bad enough.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Panagiotis Klivokiotis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36096534"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:37:05Z","content":"It is a terrible situation.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Crystal Boyd","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78867686"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:54:39Z","content":"I am a mother myself and reading about this Mom's and her family's struggle breaks my heart! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Simone Butters","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39396372"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:38:35Z","content":"for her son","like_count":0,"author_name":"kristina clark","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78764167"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T21:48:52Z","content":"Justine needs to be home for Cameron's funeral. \r\n\r\nCanadian Embassy is HEARTLESS !!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Thunder Jack","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56198673"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T23:58:25Z","content":"No one should have to go through this. It's inhumane !","like_count":0,"author_name":"Aline Schwab","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30568293"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:57:25Z","content":"I can't even begin to imagine the pain of losing one of my children... let alone not being able to be at their service to say goodbye and begin the process of grieving.  I pray that I never have to know Justine's pain. Canada - be Canadian!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tanja McCallum","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65387588"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:07:27Z","content":"No matter what the situation is, fault or not at fault, this woman deserves to be home with her loved ones to say her final good bye to her son. No parent should EVER out live their child. This is a tragic situation and she deserves at the very least, closure. Please get her home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Meaghan Shepherd","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78890039"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:43:45Z","content":"She should be able to greive with family and friends where she lives. The rest can be sorted out later.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christine Blumenfield","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78893729"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:52:49Z","content":"she is mourning and deserves to be home not in that god forsaken place","like_count":0,"author_name":"andrew jones","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78894599"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:58:33Z","content":"Why should they be allowed to prolong her agony?  Just let her get home and be done with it!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sonya Randall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78895206"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:31:56Z","content":"In cases of emergency Canadian embassies must extend full support with out fail. Humanity first.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mohammad Khan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48325146"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:21:32Z","content":"I am a mother, and I would not want to be separated from my child, whether alive or dead.  It is despicable to not allow a mother to attend her child's funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julie  Gara","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7254087"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:06:11Z","content":"Parents need to grieve the loss of a child and be at the burial. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dolores Paphites","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78914143"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:32:17Z","content":"<a href=\"mailto:denbrin@hotmail.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">denbrin@hotmail.com</a>","like_count":0,"author_name":"Denise Brind amour","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43654460"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07