ery nice. I hope the Cuban government can show some compassion in this case and expedite a tourist who is is need. I am sure the outcome will affect my desire to visit Cuba again.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dennis Chan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78897105"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:17:20Z","content":"TO BE KIND AND MORAL","like_count":0,"author_name":"NANCY STRAUB","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78905771"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:30:26Z","content":"The thought of a  mother losing her child is unthinkable but to not be there when her child is put to rest is on fathomable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sharon McMurter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63083675"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:44:40Z","content":"I can't imagine what losing my child would do to me. However, not getting a chance to say goodbye with the support of family and friends would be unbearable. It would be complete and utter cruelty to prevent a mother from burying her child due to \"red tape\".","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lacey Fontaine","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76758640"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T14:23:24Z","content":"this is outrages and the canadian government should step in","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mary-Anne  Froebe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12432325"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:22:35Z","content":"This is heart breaking!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cindy Donaldson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41507601"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:47:16Z","content":"It is inhumane to keep this mother from her baby's funeral :( Please?!!???","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cassandra Deveau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78858013"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:10:57Z","content":"Such a tragedy!  Cuba needs to let this woman say her final goodbyes to her son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Meredith Squires","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59050334"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:17:32Z","content":"This government h