nt should miss their child's funeral nor be denied the right to say goodbye.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michelle Brown","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65735320"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T03:33:56Z","content":"Human suffering is never ok. this woman is suffering, her heart is bleeding from the death of her son and Cuban authorities don't even have the compassion to even let her grieve let alone bury her little boy this is sickening and absolutely disgraceful and should be taken very seriously. This is disgusting and cold and ruthless!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anthony Williams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78804056"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:05:45Z","content":"Her being held captive is illegal.  How can these third world countries get away with this?  Where is the justice?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Diane Jones","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78896014"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T04:30:32Z","content":"Free Justine Davis, allow her to attend her son's funeral!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deborah Stevens-Balmer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78808431"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T05:18:52Z","content":"she has been through enough pain to be detained in Cuba. she needs to be able to leave the country immediately","like_count":0,"author_name":"Corinne Malca","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78811553"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:54:24Z","content":"First of all, a mother should never have to bury a child and if she has to; she holds every right to. This is HER BABY and she deserves to say goodbye just like any other mother.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Moranda Twyman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14009745"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:03:30Z","content":"Wow, i was just in Cuba with my 5 year old daughter, and i cannot even imagine anything like this happening to us. Please do the right thing, I'm totally crushed to hear about this. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rosita Stone Gomez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34430500"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:10:26Z","content":"This is ridiculous!  Canadians need some protection against corrupt/unfair legal practices in other countries.  She needs to at least be able to attend the funeral, even if Canadian officials agree to extradite her back to Cuba for the trial if there will be any.... ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Charlene Arrieta","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58798347"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:14:36Z","content":"This young mother is already dealing with her childs tragic death, it is painful enough for anyone to bear with that, and I will be praying that her heart and soul finds peace and that this beautiful little boy stay always by his mothers side as he flies with the angels. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carmen Edwards","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78905359"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:21:07Z","content":" Because I would want the same desire to come home for my childs funeral","like_count":0,"author_name":"Margaret Crouse","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47183176"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:42:22Z","content":"A friend of mine was stuck in India after a serious car accident with a large truck that killed the driver of the cab he was riding in. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Helga Brendel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73251594"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:56:39Z","content":"No mom should have to go through this. My deepest sympathies to Justine and Cameron's family","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patricia Odgers","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69355322"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:34:12Z","content":"Because this women lost her child and she should be able to return to lay her baby to rest.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melissa Vincent","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78746693"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:38:49Z","content":"She deserves to be home to burry her son. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hilary Murphy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7149874"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:47:22Z","content":"Respectful of a young mothers rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cindy Ferguson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6080997"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:18:06Z","content":"It would be disgraceful if we don't help this woman,","like_count":0,"author_name":"John Canavan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/55982983"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:42:52Z","content":"This lady should be able to come home and say her final goodbye to her baby, and have him laid to rest, she needs this.  God Bless....","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nancy Beaucage","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71124842"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:45:25Z","content":"no parent should have to say good bye to child and stay behind the last good bye should be when the parent leaves the child and for a mother not to be able to say good bye to her son and be help in a different country that isnt her's that isnt right the invesitgation should be done and she should not be held any long the family held off the funeral for her but for her not to be aloud to come back to family and her home that is just pathetic she should be home and with family at this time of need ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Krislyn Seward","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78765090"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T02:55:05Z","content":"If this woman doesn't make it home in time for her sons funeral I will have lots all respect for our government. \nLazy assholes! \nMay leave be with the entire family &lt;3 :(","like_count":0,"author_name":"Breanne Wilken","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78800871"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:52:09Z","content":"She needs closure and she has suffered enough already with her decision.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marisela Vega","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/53891300"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:05:45Z","content":"I would do the same for my child...our government sucks...\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"June Johnson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73083277"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:12:33Z","content":"This is important because this can happen to anyone one and as a mother she need to put her son to rest.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gianina Delgado","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78905040"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:01:41Z","content":"Have a frigging Heart People this is her child, Why the hell are they holding her anyway, I guess Cuba should not be a great place to Vacation then.","like_count":0,"author_name":"brenda kells","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28550292"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:42:23Z","content":"Absolutely heart breaking. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kay Chuck","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77687580"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T16:03:25Z","content":"She is a Canadian and she has been through enough.I would hope if I was in a similar situation people would care enough to help me","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shelley Richardson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78724033"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:56:40Z","content":"This is a matter of fair and timely justice. And, if this is any indication of the way Canadians are treated in Cuba, I certainly will react negatively to any fellow Canadians who are thinking about go to Cuba for their holidays.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Grant Linney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36486175"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:55:29Z","content":"I know this person well and how good this person is. She does not deserve this treatment and should be free to take care of the arrangement of her sons burial! This is so wrong on so many levels","like_count":0,"author_name":"robert lescinsky","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78863211"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:56:10Z","content":"Bring her home!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deborah Rankin Bell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39085220"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T01:21:03Z","content":"I can't begin to think about what she's going through . To lose her son & not be with him for the closure she will never get over . Please send her home . Just consider if this was your child . Hugs to you Justine &lt;3   ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andrea  Dupuis ","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28274028"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:12:42Z","content":"I am a Mom and cannot imagine what this family is going through ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jo-Anne McLean","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38684570"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T02:29:34Z","content":"Useless bureaucracy of this nature is shameful.  The mother should be released immediately to be in attendance at her son's funeral.  She has suffered enough!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ronald McGurk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57528172"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:30:56Z","content":"I too lost a son. And I have Cuban friends who would want Justine to be able to come home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Helen Forsey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78617653"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:03:14Z","content":"It's important for I am a mother and grandmother.  Justine needs closure and be able to say goodbye in this way to her precious son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mary Reiter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78895740"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:46:17Z","content":"I am cuban mother as well and I couldn't imagine the dispear she feels. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"rosalinda delgado","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78901082"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:52:24Z","content":"Because Justine needs to be with her friends and family.  She needs to be at her son's funeral!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Denise Greiner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78902048"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:07:41Z","content":"Not right to keep a mom away from her baby.","like_count":0,"author_name":"elbisa hasanbegovic","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78914440"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:15:45Z","content":"It is important for everyone to have the right to attend their child's funeral.  It is already horrific enough","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melany Henkels","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78915977"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:19:40Z","content":"It is important for this mother to be able to say goodbye to her darling little boy.","like_count":0,"author_name":"BEV  KOHUT","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21791679"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:25:47Z","content":"Her rights are been violated.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mario Mendez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73295484"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:50:30Z","content":"well i dont want it happen to me","like_count":0,"author_name":"adrienne mcmurran","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/55683689"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:56:33Z","content":"family","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tamara Forster","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38024118"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:16:22Z","content":"It is tragic that a mother has to bury her child, what is more tragic is that she cannot be at the funeral.  As a mother myself I think that would just be unbearable.  Please help Justine Davis come home!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Helen Vakalopoulos","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26920761"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:48:09Z","content":"She deserves to say goodbye to her son. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jelena Brkic","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62455830"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:21:30Z","content":"I am a mother and I couldn't imagine what she is going through.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rahel Levesque","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76967814"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:46:26Z","content":"Because it is the right thing to do!  Can't imagine how difficult this is for the family and friends.  My thoughts and prayers are with them","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Hegseth","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/53108454"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:55:06Z","content":"that was an accident; mother deserve to be with the child","like_count":0,"author_name":"Annette Bautista","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78894854"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T04:08:12Z","content":"Justine should be allowed to be at her son's funeral","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anna Hauber","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5876003"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:16:24Z","content":"She needs to be home! She needs to be with friends and family. Please she just lost her son. Let her go and be there for his funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gale Mason","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16520799"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:23:10Z","content":"The Cuban Government needs to recognize that this was an accident and not a murder.  She needs to be in Canada now to give her son the funeral he deserves with his mothers presence.  Once he is laid to rest, she can then be with her family during this trying time to get thru the lengthy grieving process.","like_count":0,"author_name":"A.R. Spiegel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78898016"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:28:20Z","content":"no mother should miss her childs funeral!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Richelle Allen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69288289"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:46:17Z","content":"I sympathise with a mother's anguish.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Selena Crosson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34393515"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:57:33Z","content":"A mother shouldn't have to bury her child before she is buried, let alone not be there to say goodbye to her lovely child for the last time.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Campbell Rees","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43584250"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:11:35Z","content":"This lady had lost her husband in november and now her child and she wont be able to get a chance to say good bye at his funeral. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Robert Curto","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65371657"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:42:26Z","content":"It  is only right that closure be given to this woman.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Thomas Johnston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69271829"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:11:52Z","content":"I am a mum, breaks my heart to read this ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Claire Girvan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/54257814"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:54:12Z","content":"she just lost her son in a different country have some kind of human compassion/empathy and bring her and her son who passed away in front of her!","like_count":0,"author_name":"kristel delisle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78749500"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:35:36Z","content":"Humanitarian aid to a Canadian citizen","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stephen van Beek","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58309546"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:23:17Z","content":"Because I know what she is going through a death in the family is the hardest thing in the world especially when it is a child.  As parents it is the most difficult thing to bury your child and for not able to be there at her sons funeral that is unacceptable when it comes to the Cuban laws. She is such a young mom and to loose the most precious thing in her life I think the Cuban should show a little compassion.  My heart goes out to you Justine.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Waheeda Khan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78885922"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:40:04Z","content":"Because I believe that this poor women has suffered a loss greater then most would ever imagine to face to spend a short three years with something you love more dearly then life itself. She needs to be able to grieve with her family and people who love her and can support her. I believe it was their fault the men in the truck and that is the reasoning behind them not releasing her home. This is an outrage and I will never travel to Cuba I do not support the system they run off. Send our citizen back home to us where we can properly care for her because it is clear cuba cannot they have taken more then words can even describe. SEND HER HOME ","like_count":0,"author_name":"victoria butler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57177918"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T01:17:04Z","content":"Purely insane, our government dips in my pockets every week charging me to work here while paying others to sit and collect welfare and this is the support they give their citizens.....","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cory Kingston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41463518"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T01:26:37Z","content":"She lost her son, isn't that enough?","like_count":0,"author_name":"jacqualine currie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48517774"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T02:42:46Z","content":"Canadian tourists are vital to the Cuban economy and should be treated with far greater respect and in this situation compassion.  The treatment Ms. Davis is receiving is hideous at best.","like_count":0,"author_name":"janet smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78799821"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:03:33Z","content":"Please make things right. Losing a kid is a parent's worst nightmare. Please help Justine attend her son's funeral. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emmanuel Filos","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74780983"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:36:09Z","content":"She's a mother who had a tragic accident while on vacation.  Cuba shouldn't detain her her without cause.  Let her bury her son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heidi brannin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78908923"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:25:48Z","content":"so she can have closure im sure she is being hard enough on herself for the accident ","like_count":0,"author_name":"frank natole","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78917988"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T13:32:23Z","content":"poor Mother shouldnt have to burry her child this young, but should most definitely be there for his funeral!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Kentner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50603174"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:40:12Z","content":"This is an outrage! Bad enough she lost her SON! She thought he would be safe sadly.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Fisher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78920702"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T14:38:53Z","content":"This mother deserves to bury her son.  She is suffering enough","like_count":0,"author_name":"Theresa Cassidy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38661053"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:33:56Z","content":"This is disgraceful behaviour by the Canadian Government and its representatives abroad.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Paula Paine","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60067328"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:35:39Z","content":"A mother should not miss her son's funeral and should not be detained in Cuba","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christine Rutter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77367566"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:44:04Z","content":"I am very sorry for your loss Justine and my heart and thoughts and prayers are with you and your family and sending positive energy that you make it back for your wee angels send off...Please know he will be with you forever and always and take comfort knowing one day you will see each other again....Love and light with peace and hugs ...take care","like_count":0,"author_name":"Claire Blanchard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27185695"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:56:13Z","content":"Because our representation of Canadians in trouble abroad is deplorable.  It is pure red-tape and ignorance that this woman cannot be with her son right  now.","like_count":0,"author_name":"joyce bogert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7493273"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T02:48:53Z","content":"As a frequent traveler to Cuba, and as a Canadian, I am appalled that this young lady is being left and ignored by her country in a Country we as a whole, love and send many visitors to annually.  Why is this happening?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amelia McLeod","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78800343"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:03:15Z","content":"She needs to be home for her childs burial, she needs to know she is there for him, any mother would need family and friends to help her get thru this.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Francine Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45090126"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:16:25Z","content":"We need to be able to trust that our country will take care of us when tragedy strikes while we are travelling.  This mother has the right to bury her son.  It's scary to think that any Canadian could be held in another country with essentially zero support from our government.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rachel Flewelling","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78897336"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:23:13Z","content":"because she is a mom that has just lost ehr child and she has a right to attend his funeral\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"lori townsend","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78898021"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:03:34Z","content":"As a single mom of four children I cannot fathom the loss this woman has suffered. It has to be unconscionable and unbearable all at the same time. If anyone out there has a heart...please send this loving mom home to bury her son and obtain closure to this tragic situation. Her journey toward healing is only beginning and to have her wrestle with these easily managed delays and  heartless uncertainties, at the start, is simply inhuman.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sharonda Scroggins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78903756"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:06:12Z","content":"I am a mother.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michael Marotte","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36794238"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:08:15Z","content":"This women needs her family & friends at this time & needs to go home & say goodbye to her son. Come on people, have a heart!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debbie Lee","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78904430"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:42:04Z","content":"Accidents happen but the government, of any country, should be sympathetic to victim's plight and tragedy and be expedite the legal process especially the victim is from a different country, and not follow the slow procedures for the sake of the process and not for the sake of the victim.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nabil Altai","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15915976"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:59:46Z","content":"For humanitarian reson","like_count":0,"author_name":"Louis Otis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77545086"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T12:37:03Z","content":"sympathy","like_count":0,"author_name":"Meghan Rothenberg","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48492805"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:03:44Z","content":"no one should be treated like this..if Canada wont stand up for its own...we as Canadians have to do the standing together!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Romeo Montague","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52573207"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:53:35Z","content":"Sympathy, empathy, human solidarity...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne Levasseur","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69516145"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:58:30Z","content":"I'M CANADIAN","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandra Graham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68333244"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:47:06Z","content":"This is barbaric! Send her home!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brenda Pollard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15610143"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:19:00Z","content":"Justice and compassion","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tim Gaudet","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16869709"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:28:08Z","content":"basic compassion","like_count":0,"author_name":"brooke hodgins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35677578"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:03:15Z","content":"It\u2019s her baby; she didn't want her baby to die. Let her go!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rachel Caldwell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78895743"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:44:10Z","content":"No mother wants to out live her kids that is enough on her as it is please let her say Good bye to her baby","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tannisha Phelps","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78910117"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:09:35Z","content":"I have a 4 year old son, this is such a tragic story that has hit close to home for me. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jenee Bounville","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78914808"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:42:28Z","content":"It is her son and he is in his home country and she should be wih him. Omg","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sharon Hutchings","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60517080"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:11:52Z","content":"It is outrageous that someone who has committed no crime and is herself a victim is being detained in a foreign country, particularly under these tragic circumstances.  Please do the right thing and intervene on her behalf.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pat Brown","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21847337"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:02:19Z","content":"As a mother I can't even imagine going through what she's going through.  She did nothing wrong & should be allowed to come home & attend her son's funeral.  Have a heart.","like_count":0,"author_name":"melanie bolohan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35900855"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:54:15Z","content":"Please allow Justine to come home for her son's funeral. This is so heartbreaking and undeserved. A mother needs to be allowed closure in such a life changing event. Make it happen please","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sherry  Vervaecke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2260621"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:06:39Z","conte