ET THIS POOR WOMAN GO HOME TO HER FAMILY TO BURY HER BABY!!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"DEBORAH REYNOLDS","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78903446"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:53:07Z","content":"because every mother deserves one last goodbye.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emily Sanginesi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76752664"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:17:44Z","content":"Because it is a human right to say goodbye to our loved ones","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marie Dupuis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/64488446"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:34:01Z","content":"Heart felt sympathies","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maria Braganza","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65052669"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:43:53Z","content":"Is is the right thing to do....morally and ethically!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lorrie Clark","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48535743"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:21:19Z","content":"If the Government of Canada has any compassion and/or concern regarding its citizens in other countries surely there can be no more pressing case to apply all due means to persuade the Cuban authorities to allow Justine to attend her son's funeral","like_count":0,"author_name":"Adrian Gordon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16346246"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:48:22Z","content":"Because no one deserves such a tragic loss. none the less not being able to have closure towards someone more valuable than anything in the world.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah Toor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65752378"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:30:35Z","content":"A mother has a many god given rights.  The right to bury her child is sad but no less true.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stephen Spriggs","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78763058"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:26:33Z","content":"No parent should have to bury their child, but if they do, they need to be there for closure ","like_count":0,"author