,"content":"Let her go home bury her son. Give her Closure","like_count":0,"author_name":"ken Webber","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78907545"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:05:46Z","content":"no parent should have to bury their child  , in a case unfortunatly that happens and this ladiy deserves to be at her son's funeral !   BRING HER HOME !  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"jo-ann silver","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78914056"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:29:05Z","content":"It important for her to be back in Canada for the funeral of her son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andre Cormier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59906955"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:59:39Z","content":"This sad event makes me question if I would want to go on a holiday to Cuba, if this is what can happen.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pauline Robert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62886483"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:00:53Z","content":"for so many reasons but first and foremost this young lady needs to be home with her family. This is such a tragic story.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kim Frattura","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48104615"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:29:39Z","content":" No mother should every be denied to go to her son funeral.\r\nShe is in a bad country. I don't understand. Why people want to go into a place like this one.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carol Davies","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6854350"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:48:24Z","content":"Because she gave him life. She needs peace to accept him gone. Set aside politics...family is the most important thing.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Grace Gilmore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75149044"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:34:01Z","content":"we must look after all our citizens in distress-it is the humanitarian and patriotic thing to do.","like_count":0,"author_name":"conrad lewis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78286822"},{"created_at":"2014-02-