y!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Luke Empey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73915218"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:39:08Z","content":"A child is part of you - there is no way she should miss his funeral","like_count":0,"author_name":"Myrna Kosloski","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74689326"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:19:12Z","content":"Everyone has the right to be at their family members funeral! Especially if its their child being buried! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bartlomiej Wnek","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14481080"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:23:25Z","content":"Because I am a MOTHER!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joanne Whiffin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77481178"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:42:13Z","content":"She needs closer it is a horrific situation and needs to get home to family and friends so can cared for.  Losing a child is the hardest thing in the world cannot imagine what she is going through - prayers going her way.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maria Melo Muina","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77482453"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:25:59Z","content":"This is a terrible tragedy and she needs to be with her family. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lorey Throgmartin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78907212"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:28:02Z","content":"love has no borders","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bella Grundy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28590124"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:38:16Z","content":"I am a mother and a grandmother and cannot be anything but outraged that this mother cannot be a her own child's funeral.  I think she has gone thru enough.  Help her.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan Dranez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47216651"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T13:08:07Z","content":"It is important to do the best thing for humanity. Even if Cuba flies her back after the funeral, closure and sentimental peace is the least this grieving mother should be 