acy... ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lew Cline","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34759310"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:29:51Z","content":"Her son died, she should be able to say goodbye the proper way us Canadians do...please free her immediately!!\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"LueAnne Osterhout","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72865779"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:36:01Z","content":"Saying goodbye to a loved one is so important, but when it's your own small child, the mother MUST be there. Please help her!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michelle Healey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14228743"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:55:26Z","content":"iT IS IMPORTANT AS THIS IS ANOTHER EXAMPLE OF THE CORRYPTION AND VILOTATION OF HUMAN RIGHTS IN CUBA","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jose Escalante","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78877023"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:01:31Z","content":"I have moved from Edmonton and not living in Penticton BC - kindly edit .  Joy","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joy Sparks","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36783429"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:02:10Z","content":"this should be important to everyone, because if i was in her position....well it's self explanatory.","like_count":0,"author_name":"chris cruickshank","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78786288"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:39:39Z","content":"This is a sin let her be with her child :(","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pam Shubrook","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78789592"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T01:07:32Z","content":"My goodness. The pain and loss this mother must be feeling. My heart and prayers go out to her and her family. Canadians have more lobe and respect for our fellow Canadians and our children than this. Please for the love of children bring this woman home. As a mother myself this is just unimaginable. If I could wrap my heart around you and take it all back I cetsinly would. Our government boasts supporting their people.