 mother needs some closure by saying goodbye to her son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brandy Baker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78903391"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:10:01Z","content":"no mother should have to miss her own childs funeral....bad enough she lost him so early in llife....god bless her and family!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"stephanie newell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78904599"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T16:16:00Z","content":"This woman has lost her child let her say good bye at least!! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Angel Chr\u00e9tien","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78725888"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:42:09Z","content":"This is one of the instances when we need our government to look after our needs and they are failing.  I want to help pressure them to act and help this family.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cindy Cnider","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60747887"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:07:59Z","content":"Why are they keeping her in Cuba? She was a visitor. If able to fly she should be transported home","like_count":0,"author_name":"Wendy Percy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/55952172"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T23:56:50Z","content":"Have traveled to Cuba often and would not want to ever be in her position. What a tragedy!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lynn Adams-Dunn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56233496"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:06:25Z","content":"It's not fair for a bereaved mother to be prevented from attending her son's funeral for some political reason she has no part in- get her back fast please!!!\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maribeth Curry","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52683659"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:12:24Z","content":"Bring this mother home to her baby and family. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Katie Kelly","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78890535"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T01:59:32Z","content":"Family friend and my son used to play with baby Cameron am a mom I feel  Justin's pain","like_count":0,"author_name":"coryse felix","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78796208"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:30:19Z","content":"I am a mom and I would want to be able to come home to say goodbye please have a heart and send her home","like_count":0,"author_name":"PAula Veinotte Nickerson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57295686"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:54:39Z","content":"As a mother I cannot imagine this horrific ordeal.  SOMEBODY has got to be able to help this poor woman.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Leah Rouse","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26775111"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:05:19Z","content":"I am a mother. If I were to lose a child, I would NEED family support.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Yadira Guzman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15335697"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:22:29Z","content":"She already lost her son which is a terrible thing for a mother and now Cuban government wants to just hold her for no reason.  Ridiculous.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rick Luthra","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78897961"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T05:01:05Z","content":"It is truly a sad day when signatures are what's required in order for our government to do the right thing. Canada and Cuba have an exceptional relationship, and there should be no reason for our government not to intervene.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Robert Andersen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78810483"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:58:39Z","content":"Because I am mother who has lost a child...And it is a parents worst nightmare. She needs closure to move on.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cynthia Thompson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76316180"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:14:21Z","content":"The gov't are appointed trustees to protect our assets and protect us from harm.  They are failing the duties of their offices badly!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Robyn Garlough","