e is a wonderful person.     Ashley Bender","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ashley Bender","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78853069"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:01:16Z","content":"It is unconscionable that the Canadian government is not doing everything they can to assist Canadians in trouble abroad.  As a Canadian citizen, responsible for paying the salaries of our politicians, I demand action on behalf of Justine Davis.  It is ridiculous that nothing has been done.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joyce Schafers","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66729395"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:30:36Z","content":"Of course she wants to be with her son. so sad. Hope she gets home. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rachel LeBlanc","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70251671"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:58:52Z","content":"I'm a mom","like_count":0,"author_name":"megan Hourie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68951808"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:12:48Z","content":"laws have to be human and consider this special case","like_count":0,"author_name":"therese Francoz","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63476721"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:03:13Z","content":"How sad! What has she done that's so wrong?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Diane Racine","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72755879"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:42:13Z","content":"Good luck Justine ! Our Canadian Government have loose his heart !","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marcel Lapierre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36448733"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T21:38:51Z","content":"as a parent, I believe she needs to be there and I am sure she really needs to be with family....","like_count":0,"author_name":"caroline rands","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14957342"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:39:40Z","content":"It is social injustice.  We have bigger things to worry about, it's taking care of our own.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Holly McNaughton","author_url":"http://api.change.