d to come home to see him burried...  We as Canadians have to bring her home so she can make peace with what has happened.  I believe all Canadians would wish the same if they were in this situation!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melissa Ziegler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78755103"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:13:59Z","content":"this mother should be able to say goodbye to her son... please let her go.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Louise Lapierre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65277683"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:42:06Z","content":"JUSTINE IS A FRIEND OF OUR FAMILY AND EVEN IF SHE WASN'T, THIS IS MOST HORRIFIC STORY I HAVE EVER HEARD!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"MARGO CLOUTIER","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78873631"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:43:18Z","content":"How is it possible that this woman can not be home to burry her child? Are you kidding me? Please get her home so that she can be with her son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andrianna Kissavos","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41756720"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:37:58Z","content":"Because this is an outrage! Canadian government - step up!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carly Charlebois","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66690931"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:21:36Z","content":"Human rights are at stake!  A suffering mother and poor lost child are at the hands of Government Officials that have no decency.  Why does Canada have Agencies and Embassy's in place to help and protect our citizens if they DONT ACTUALLY WORK???? I am broken hearted for this poor mother and family! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Trisha MacIntyre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78891472"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:54:42Z","content":"She a Mother, show passion  toward her, its call empathy.","like_count":0,"author_name":"ELOUISEMCC MCCRAY","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1255578"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:33:54Z","content":"because this is wrong","like_count":