with her.   This was a tragic accident and Cuban officials should be ashamed of themselves for containing a grieving mother.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elfreida Jeffries","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78900683"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:08:05Z","content":"Let this Mother be with her baby, 'one' more time.. Condolences to Justine and her family...","like_count":0,"author_name":"ANNE MORAN","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68981271"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:46:08Z","content":"I'm a mother. It's hard to comprehend how she must feel after losing her baby, let alone not being able to be with him while he's put to rest. She's alone and needs people around her who love her and loved Cameron. This is heartbreaking and I'm begging for someone to let this woman go home. She will never completely be the same and this is only making it worse.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shanine Bright","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78910453"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:05:31Z","content":"Justice, truth","like_count":0,"author_name":"Allyson Linklater","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71202728"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T13:11:26Z","content":"Get this woman home. No excuses. This is ridiculous!! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kristen Flake","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76942573"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T11:43:32Z","content":"My heart goes out to her,no mother should have to go through this..having to say good-bye to your child is hard enough...not being there would be horrible :'( &lt;3","like_count":0,"author_name":"Irene Junnola-Nagy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78838006"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:35:08Z","content":"another reason why I will never visit Cuba","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bruce Bowman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9722559"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:08:14Z","content":"COMMON SENSE SHOULD PREVAIL IN SUCH MATTERS","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michael Holubik","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73999646"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:25:20Z","content":"It is a simple matter of human compassion, this is unbelievable!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Neil Mudde","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31865074"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:40:38Z","content":"Let this poor girl come home, what a tragic incident she needs her family, and say goodbye to her baby boy! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christiane Nunn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78756150"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T21:47:54Z","content":"cause i am a mother and would be devastated from this if it was to happen to me .......... bring her home to see her damnnn son whats wrong with this world","like_count":0,"author_name":"chantal poulin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78771850"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T23:45:06Z","content":"I am a mum too!!  So wrong!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Donna Johnson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78784766"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T05:17:53Z","content":"Why is this important to me? This should be important to anyone with basic morals and understanding,It's a rather complex situation. Look at the picture of it? The crisp cuba sun is shining down on my face,as lizards cross the streets and the local cubans great you willingy,you rent a vehicle to travel the beautiful land to only find your self in accident,broken bones on a foreign island,you awake to find out your three year old has passed away and you might not make it  home to get your final closure,  To only think your giving a country that's main source of income is from tourism.. Yet they treat Tourist as criminals for getting in a car accident,Do you notice the \"Accident\" part at the end of car? I'm simply outraged by this story and Justine Davis needs to be home!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Judson Perry","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78811498"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:43:50Z","content":"Okay, I'm signing this petition, but I have something to say first.  I am tired of people continuing to travel to Cuba, only to get into some sort of terrible accident, or complication of some sort which enables the Cuban government to detain those people in Cuba for as long as they feel like keeping them there.  Now I know that many of you will think that I am kicking someone when they are down, that is not the case.  I, of course want Justine to come home.  I feel for her, she is the victim here, I am not blaming her, but when are people going to realize that Cuba is a communist country.  It is run by dictators who deny rights to their own citizens and if you are a visitor, you are completely at their mercy. People should be very afraid to travel to Cuba.  There have been many incidents of vacationers who have been involved in accidents, and have been detained until their case has been heard in court, or until hospital and other fees have been paid.  Nineteen year old Cody LeCompte was detained for over 4 months after he was broadsided by a truck, and faced up to three years in jail.  This is no more than blackmail, and historically, the Canadian government is powerless to help.  We, in Canada have no leverage to force Cuba to release anyone.  Unless the Canadian government boycotts travel to Cuba, which would impact their economy negatively, we have nothing to bargain with.  I hope and pray that the Canadian Ambassador can do something.  Canadians need to stay the hell out of Cuba.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Suzette Heine","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45931521"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:10:12Z","content":"I wish my signature will make the difference for Justine Davis, I offer my sympathies to her and her family ! God Bless !\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"eliane themistocle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45487292"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T15:50:23Z","content":"i beleive holding a mother back from her own childs funeral is more then torture.","like_count":0,"author_name":"corey pember","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78721976"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:02:11Z","content":"This is an outrage and the Cuban authorities should be ashamed of themselves. Get this woman back so she can bury her son!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chris Moor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28416781"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:56:13Z","content":"I'm a mother and this is so tragic! Canada needs to have her released from Cuban authorities ASAP to be with her family in Canada at this time of grief and sadness","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karen Whiteduck","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47319481"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:30:52Z","content":"Decency!","like_count":0,"author_name":"ileana doclin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62863390"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:06:14Z","content":"As Cuba seeks better access to the world, with the help of Canada, now is the time to allow this bereaved mother to go home.  Holding her hostage to outmoded bureaucracy will satisfy no one.  Release Justine Davis now!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carolyn MacLeod","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24544670"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:58:57Z","content":"Please allow this woman to come home.  She's guilty of no wrong doing, and has earned the right to come and bury her child, and convalesce with friends and family","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sara Lima Branco","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13892017"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:21:47Z","content":"Justine is a Canadian who needs proper medical and emotional support.  They can deal with the legal issues afterwards.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christine Cooper","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21794109"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:31:14Z","content":"This story is so sad that reading it changed my mood completely... please let her go","like_count":0,"author_name":"Luka Scepanovic","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5079738"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:26:45Z","content":"Her human rights are being violated. 