h. My heart aches for her :(","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Miller","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78790120"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T01:00:18Z","content":"Justine is a friend of mine and i also just lost my younger sister who lives in the U.S.> i have been refused permission to enter the states before but was allowed to enter for my sisters funeral. It would have really upset me if i couldnt go. Now i feel as if Justine's situation is worse. this is her son and only child losing him must be bad enough but to never see him again is ridiculous she should have been let go a long time ago.","like_count":0,"author_name":"IAN WALKER","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78791187"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T01:07:53Z","content":"Why is Canada not supporting it's citizens?  Why is Cuba detaining this mother?  Seems like bureaucracy gone awry -- have some compassion!! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dr. Elizabeth Weber Wheaton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14362336"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:16:41Z","content":"This grieving mother should be at home surrounded by family and friends after such a tragedy.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sabrina K. Raulerson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78905671"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:20:59Z","content":"A mother should be at her son's funeral.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kendra Neuman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78906337"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:33:54Z","content":"She needs to be with her son so she can have peace with her son and be there she desevers to be let her go be with her son","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cassandra Gaudaur","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78908556"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:48:11Z","content":"No reason for Cuba to keep her there, so sad","like_count":0,"author_name":"Agnes Hanlon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66988559"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T15:12:47Z","content":"Let the mother to say \"good buy\" to her son","like_count":0,"au