","content":"Because I am a traveller also, and if something like this happened to me or my family, my government, that I pay taxes too, and vote in, should help.  I aswell am a mother, and can't imagine how Justine is feeling.  To lose a child, in a foreign country, not able to grieve with her family around her to help, is just awful.  Please help get her papers to come home - to Canada.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sylvia Brewer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16850183"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:21:42Z","content":"Please work to have the Cuban Government release Justine Davis on compassionate grounds at the very least.  This woman has been through enough trauma with the loss of her father and loss of her son on what was supposed to be a wonderful trip.  She is a Canadian and it is the Canadian Government's obligation to protect its citizens around the world from undemocratic government systems.  Cuba relies heavily on Canadian tourism.  If they don't release her, the Canadian government can put heavy pressure on them because of the tourism economy that our country provides to them.  Bring her home NOW!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michelle Quattrociocchi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44529164"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:00:47Z","content":"She needs to attend her only sons funeral ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hailey Sutej","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78859127"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:38:42Z","content":"Its all about family in the time of need.Please let her come home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"sandy mimra","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71558132"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:34:03Z","content":"What on earth is going on there???","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gaston Synnott","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3277563"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:07:22Z","content":"this girl need to get home so she can lay her sweet babe to rest....please help her!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"wendy c Dodge","author