:0,"author_name":"JEAN-PIERRE-BRAZEAU JEAN-PIERRE-BRAZEAU","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59554321"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:53:22Z","content":"A person is there when their child is born and should be there when there child passes away.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Darlene Kiley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77590670"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:00:25Z","content":"We need accountability from our Canadian embassies. Tell us why she isn't allowed home yet.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shalini Roy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78852881"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:31:20Z","content":"My heart goes out to your family. Such a tragic loss and to have to go through all this is such an injustice. I am disgusted that our government hasn't stepped in - such a simple matter to solve.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandi nelles","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21015272"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:42:09Z","content":"Do not strain friendly relations between Cuba & Canada but this inaction which might lead other Canadians to think twice about visiting Cuba.","like_count":0,"author_name":"charles Bull","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/67971431"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:39:11Z","content":"I feel that the Canadian government has a duty and responsibility to do everything in its power to help it's citizens deal with difficult foreign governments when issues arise, especially if these issues are not wilfully caused by the involved citizens, such as is the case in this instance.","like_count":0,"author_name":"JOHN DAMOISEAUX","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66757674"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:23:43Z","content":"If Justine is not allowed to leave Cuba to attend her son's funeral I will never travel to Cuba and will tell my friends not to travel there, as I do regarding Mexico. I can't believe that after Prime Minister Trudeau was on such good terms with Castro , and with the number of tourism dollars Canadians spend in Cuba that the plight of a Canadian tourist wouldn't take priority and be addressed quickly and efficiently. I am also concerned that the Canadian Government may be skimping on funding and staffing our  embassies rendering them ineffective when it comes time to assist law abiding citizens when they get into situations such as this abroad. It appears that action is only taken when it hits the media BIG!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Glen Wright","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78878288"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:51:25Z","content":"This accident took place two months ago.  If there are no charges pending, Justine should not be denied her basic Human Right to return to her country.\r\nI am also appalled that it takes public intervention to get our Canadian Embassy to act.  I realize that local procedures must be followed but I would hope diplomatic relations should have some impact on ensuring Canadians are protected abroad.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lesley Oliver","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27506377"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:53:21Z","content":"Our country needs to start taking better care of it's citizens when they travel abroad or else Canadians will no longer feel safe leaving our own country. Please help this mother come home so she can properly put her son to rest and say goodbye. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kelly Culp","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28561223"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T03:43:14Z","content":"This needs to be sent to the Prime Ministers Office and the Leaders of the Opposition along with the Minister of Foreign Affairs ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rosalyn Forrester","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15935365"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:29:17Z","content":"I'm sorry to hear about the accident.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Fleming","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7018737"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:37:49Z","content":"Moms shoud always be with their kids\r\n","like_count":0,"author_na