ke_count":0,"author_name":"Bev Vardal","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59274454"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:11:57Z","content":"If a Canadian cannot expect some assistance in such a terrible time, then what the hell are we paying diplomatic staff for?  Get up off your duffs and make this happen for this poor woman, who is already suffering the worst loss anyone can have....","like_count":0,"author_name":"Caroline Yull","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3058917"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:55:54Z","content":"To lose a child is agony.  Justine should at least be at her boy's funeral.  The support of those who love her would mean so much to her.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jean Clayton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/55450794"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:27:04Z","content":"Let this Mom say goodbye to her son!  This is incredible that the Government will not step in!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melanie Desloges","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13274389"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:50:40Z","content":"The lack of escalation by the Harper government on this matter is deplorable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bruce Bennett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/46937751"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:41:04Z","content":"She needs to say goodbye to her son!!!! Have a heart!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Maindonald","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48432551"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T23:54:10Z","content":"Friend of a friend, and this is not right.  She should be home with her family. During this time.","like_count":0,"author_name":"aaron neal","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78785544"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:55:47Z","content":"MICHELE MCPHAIL","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michele McPhail","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72928244"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:48:28Z","content":"As a parent, I,m well aware of the stress and agony this is causing Justine","like_count":0,"author_name":"Glen A. Fox","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39738656"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:53:23Z","content":"she needs to be with her son!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Regina Pierre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78894670"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:17:21Z","content":"Canada should support Canadians in trouble, particularly when they have not committed a crime or been irresponsible.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Jones","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47206313"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:06:59Z","content":"she deserves closure","like_count":0,"author_name":"eric peterson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78904245"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:24:14Z","content":"because im a mom","like_count":0,"author_name":"kATHERINE eVANS","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51880450"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:32:55Z","content":"I can't believe this atrocity... Let her come home immediately.... No excuses!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brent Starkes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77025309"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:08:23Z","content":"Where is the compassion?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tina Dior","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41710288"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:14:28Z","content":"I am a mother and grandmother with four of my own children and 9 grandchildren. I cannot imagine even having to say a final goodbye but it is worse not even being to have the opportunity to. Part of healing over the loss of life is being able to have closure by attending the funeral. As a mother I plead on her behalf that the Canadian gov't step in and help this young mother get home to her family where she can get the love and support she desperately needs right now.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marsha Oja","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71615262"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T15:14:41Z","content":"She is my friend......she needs to come home.    We love her and want her safe.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lee Chalmers","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78716996"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T17:47:10Z","content":"so the mother can be home to bury her little angel ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gloria Drouillard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73083245"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:45:55Z","content":"As I travel a lot, inactivity of Canadian government disturbs me. And last december was first time I visited the Caribbean region","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ivan Varatsilenka","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39668706"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:51:53Z","content":"These people,employed,and paid by the taxpayers of Canada, should either work,lead or get out of the way. Do what your paid to do, help Canadians who need it within the country your are fortunate enough to be in, once again paid for by those Canadian taxpayers.","like_count":0,"author_name":"David/Joyce Baxter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60113759"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:46:18Z","content":"No mother should have to go through any thing like this ever. I am a proud Canadian, but today I feel shame in my country.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marguerite Granade","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9893480"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:22:22Z","content":"I couldn't imagine being in a different country unable to attend the funeral of my child! Heart breaking! Let her come home already!!! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dawn Redmond","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77249025"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:42:19Z","content":"Please accept our condolences","like_count":0,"author_name":"Leyla Okatan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48803056"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:01:36Z","content":"a nother should be at her sons funeral","like_count":0,"author_name":"nicole persad","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37901966"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:11:26Z","content":"Amazing what happens in these 3rd world countries. They hold our citizens hostage when there is no proof of wrongdoing","like_count":0,"author_n