f a situation and I pray for her  and her family during this time. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Holly Wilson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78808104"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:11:15Z","content":"I can only think of my own children and how I would be feeling....this is terrible","like_count":0,"author_name":"JESSICA BAGWELL","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78904850"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:17:40Z","content":"IM A MOTHER AND THIS IS TERRIBLE FOR HER TO GO THROUGH. IT WAS A TRAGIC ACCIDENT...NOTHING MORE. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"RHONDA ALLEN","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78905827"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T16:53:53Z","content":"Justine, its been 4 years since you consoled me when my daughter passed away,  and years in between, I want you tthat  you are in my heart and prayers xxx helping any way I can !!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Whitehead (Brown)","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78731586"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T16:56:48Z","content":"canadian freedom abroad","like_count":0,"author_name":"alexandra wilson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50241740"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:53:48Z","content":"Par humanit\u00e9 m\u00eame si le gouvernement canadien ne conna\u00eet pas vraiment le sens de ce mot","like_count":0,"author_name":"Henriette Therrien","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/40729134"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:09:40Z","content":"Why is she being detained?  A mother needs to be at her child's funeral!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan Eastwood","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44831033"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:12:27Z","content":"Please send her home. Nobody should have to go through this. Where is our government when we need them the most!!?!? ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Victoria Snow","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78752132"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:46:19Z","content":"This could happen to anyone. If this goes unchecked it will set a guideline for other Canadian travellers should they find themselves in the same situation. Shame on the Canadian Government for not stepping in to assist. It doesn't surprise me.......","like_count":0,"author_name":"LYNDA SQUIRES","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2712036"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:17:58Z","content":"What we are asking the Ambassador to is the the right thing!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mike Harker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75761546"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:27:05Z","content":"Family is important.  Free Justine so she can take care of hers.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tricia Smeding","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75035461"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:16:02Z","content":"A mother shouldn't be keep from her owns child's funeral and be able to say goodbye to them ","like_count":0,"author_name":"corisa dunlop","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11321016"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T22:27:57Z","content":"Let this mother go and say good bye to her son.Let the mom come home to her family.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shirley L","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78776696"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T01:18:45Z","content":"A mother should be able to bury her son.  She is a Canadian, not charged and should be free to leave Cuba.  We as Canadians should help her.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Micheline Charlebois","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78792428"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:31:56Z","content":"I'm a mother of young children myself.  I can't even imagine what this must be like for Justine and her family.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Sygo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10118621"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:44:19Z","content":"Because this is the hardest, worst thing anyone should have to go through and she needs to be there for her son. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amie Anderson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78893786"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:26:50Z","content":"We need to help one another, or else what kind of world would this be.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Maciel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78898515"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T13:48:57Z","content":"Have some heart Cuba","like_count":0,"author_name":"Yvonne D","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78708735"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T13:19:19Z","content":"This mother needs to be with her son. She needs the time to grieve to be present for her sons funeral. She should not have to live the rest of her life knowing she was not at her sons funeral!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maricela M","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78848138"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:16:24Z","content":"This woman has suffered enough.  To lose a parent is bad enough.  To lose her son is devastating.  To not be able to be with him to bury him is unjust.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kati Wade","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78860481"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:21:06Z","content":"I feel any country should have respect for who ever has a misfortune they should try everything in there power to help out. I understand there is red tape in countries but this should be priority as a human being may you have mercy on your soul. A mother has a bond like no other with a child. So give her the respect to burry her son and give her closure.    ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brenda Barker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78084490"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:18:54Z","content":"Canadian Citizens should not be detained in foreign countries without just cause.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nancie Westhaver","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47290761"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:23:59Z","content":"Cuba depends on Canadian tourism in big way.  Word gets out about this inaction, might affect the decision by many to go there. Get her home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ted Cumber","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51637844"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:08:36Z","content":"Because family matters","like_count":0,"author_name":"Daryl del Rosario","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78751620"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:42:21Z","content":"I've lost my own son. This is terrible.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ellis  Roddick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29065401"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:35:44Z","content":"You live once.... you have the right to say good bye to a love one... ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Luc Ladouceur","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78763792"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:21:32Z","content":"For the sake of appearing human let the poor woman bury her son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alan Fairweather","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58894736"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:34:13Z","content":"Because I'm a mother of a beautiful 2 1/2 years old little angel.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Annie Roy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/64748402"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:27:37Z","content":"Because I myself am a mother of a three year old son and I cannot imagine the pain that Justine Davis must feel right now. Please let her come home to say goodbye. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessica Persiel-Jones","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69954181"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:01:29Z","content":"As a mother myself, I can not comprehend the pain and suffering this woman is experiencing and to then be prevented from participating in such an important part of the grieving process? Put simply, this is inhumane.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rebecca Sumners","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20161994"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T03:23:55Z","content":"I am a Mother and my heart goes out to Justine.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deborah McDonald","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78803247"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:55:17Z","content":"Because I have 4 kids and understand how parents love there kids","like_count":0,"author_name":"Fazle Hussain","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35267699"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:57:37Z","content":"I think this is very SAD that the Cuban government is doing this to her. I will not vacation down there anymore as much as i loved it if this will not happen for her. It's unexceptionable!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dario Cingolani","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52502224"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:11:16Z","content":"Because its humanitarian that this lady have closure to her son's death to start the healing process. it is unthinkable that she is detained and worst of all the Canadian Consulate is not at the forefront of this nightmare in helping and reaching out to their own citizen. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lynden Rahming","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78904862"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:24:16Z","content":"why is she still there, she she should be back home where she belongs, sorry for you son:( may he RIP","like_count":0,"author_name":"Annie Tutunjian","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2701959"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:35:01Z","content":"she must be heart broken","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cherie Davidson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31732134"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:16:40Z","content":"Because she has been away from the people that love her long enough, she needs to be with people that can help her get through this tragedy and put her son to rest. its a sad loss. I feel for her and I wish no one had to go through this, but when god calls his angels home they must go, so he is another angel, we must pray for her. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan Radford","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78916143"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T17:22:16Z","content":"A mother should be allowed to bury her child.. Also this is a lack of human rights.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Idelia Prescott","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48510011"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:21:06Z","content":"This is a humanitarian issue. There is no threat to anyone.I urge the Canadian government to step in on her and her families behalf.","like_count":0,"author_name":"JoAnne Fleming-Valin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34258260"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:46:23Z","content":"I'm a mother of 5 and I can't not even bear to think of the pain this mother is going in through with the loss of her only child let alone imagine the heart ache of not being able to say good bye to see him one last time....my heart is so broken up by her situation and my thought and prayers go out to you in this moment of your pain and suffering:'(","like_count":0,"author_name":"maria cuadra","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78868291"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:54:55Z","content":"Because, as a mom, I cannot imagine the pain she is going through. She is a grieving mother, not a criminal...allow her to return home to put her child to rest. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julia Holman-Price","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47929560"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:12:22Z","content":"It's the right thing to do!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lorraine Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78760577"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:45:15Z","content":"No good reason to hold her. Why is it taking so long for the investigation.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patricia Houghton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74749226"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:27:45Z","content":"<a href=\"mailto:Renehug.BT@gmail.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Renehug.BT@gmail.com</a>","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rene Hug","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78271130"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:50:43Z","content":"SHE NEEDS TO BURY HER BABY.","like_count":0,"author_name":"barbara MCCAW","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78765783"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:53:13Z","content":"Because it's horrific!  The woman needs support from her family and friends....not the police or investigators....give me a break!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jacqueline Forsythe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78902206"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:58:26Z","content":"I am signing this petition because nobody should bury a chid...but also nobody should be trapped and held in a foreign country on the day that its their babys funeral either. I am sorry for your loss and I hope you have a full healing. And get to be at your sons funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deborah Henderson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78912644"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:30:57Z","content":"This story doesn't make sense.  Cuba needs to let her leave.  There is no criminal reason... this situation needs to be cleaned up\r\n ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Krista Lina  Johnston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27352557"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:51:16Z","content":"she adored her son let her leave and be with him one last time before he gets burried!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Suzette Stewart","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71856291"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:41:56Z","content":"Justine's situation is tragic, and the Government of Cuba needs to understand that it is both inexplicable and unacceptable to Canadians. I have often thought of travelling to Cuba, after many positive experiences friends have had. But I will not consider doing so until this case is resolved with priority, justice and compassion.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ben Wolfe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2638306"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:08:37Z","content":"because I am a mother and what is happening in this situation is wrong. this is devastating","like_count":0,"author_name":"daniela delpodio","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78751623"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:14:47Z","content":"Legal red tape and bureaucracy should never impede the rights of a family member to travel in an emergency.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andrew Kucy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56075000"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:15:23Z","content":"<a href=\"mailto:arlenefield@hotmail.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">arlenefield@hotmail.com</a>","like_count":0,"author_name":"Arlene Field","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7269333"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:34:16Z","content":"This woman suffered a tragic loss in an accident and should not be held in Cuba.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dolores Baily","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78876038"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:45:21Z","content":"Canadian citizens abroad should be able to expect the support of our embassies.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Louise Uhryniuk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75856012"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:41:14Z","content":"A mother tragically lost her beloved little boy and to add to the trauma Cuba is holding her back from being at her sons funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Louise Miglino","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/67712934"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:56:26Z","content":"since the mother is not being held on any charges there is NO reason why she is not already back in Canada. Passing the political buck around is against our Canadian Governments laws and rules, yet you are doing it.\r\nStop sitting on your hands and get working at getting this mother back home NOW!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debbie Thrift","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24347849"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:40:18Z","content":"I can only imagine the pain the family is in right now and anything that can help would certainly be appreciated I am sure.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Janet Barlow","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44605946"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:44:56Z","content":"I find the Canadian authorities inactive in cases involving our citizens visiting abroad. This must change. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"lorraine stiefenhofer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68950436"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:10:29Z","content":"It will be a grave set back for tourist in cuba","like_count":0,"author_name":"Edouard Robichaud","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/55575207"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:14:30Z","content":"This is horrible for a Canadian to be going though! Fix this ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amy Monteith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78915778"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:40:52Z","content":"Heartbreaking!   Let her come back and say goodbye to her son.  She needs closure.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Helen Gilmore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78862332"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:46:08Z","content":"if Cuba is looking to premote tourism is is not a very good start ! by telling tourist or other what to exspect in way of their (justice) ? system and government polaices with tourist. and a just disgraceful display of compasion for humanity.....you have a very    \r\n beautiful country rich in natural; historical charm and very warm hearted people !! ...why spoil it","like_count":0,"author_name":"keith sisson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37577585"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:14:47Z","content":"Our goverment should provide more assistance in these types of situations and every parent should be able  to attend the childs funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ron Bunclark","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78872250"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T21:31:18Z","content":"she needs to be with her son!","like_count":0,"author_name":"kristen mcnish","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78769835"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T21:58:26Z","content":"it is clear that this was simply a accident, a extremely tragic one at that. There is no reason why this grief stricken mother should not able to attend her young child's funeral. as a mother of a 2.5 year old I could only imagine the pain she must be feeling. I am sure that her injuries are but a minor paper cut compared to the injury of losing her glorious child. please please send this mother home to lay her child to rest and allow her the chance to be able to start the process of moving forward. God Bless and my thoughts and prayers are with you and your family during this difficult, unfair time.","like_count":0,"author_name":"April Fudge","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76923413"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:55:51Z","content":"I'm a mother. Enough said.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Paulina Zaborska","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48238170"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:53:28Z","content":"Cubans love and  value family greatly and would be deeply disturbed, as we are, by the fact that a mother at what has to be the most painful time in her life, the death of her child, cannot attend the funeral. Can we even begin to imagine her pain. If she needs to go back to Cuba after the funeral that is another item. Please let her say goodbye to her child.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jim Craig","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23747247"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:56:26Z","content":"it was an accident!! A mother needs to be at their childs funeral. it is not right to keep her from the service that is just being heart less.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Guillermina Grajeda","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11796218"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:35:03Z","content":"Because as a mother of three sons, and just as a person who has lost too many people in my life, being able to say goodbye to loved ones is incredibly important and necessary. If there is no just cause for keeping Justine in Cuba, her people, the place she calls home, pays taxes to, is responsible to, should also be responsible in return.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amber Hubka","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78753136"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:47:21Z","content":"this is wrong she has suffered enough","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chris Weins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71379920"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:26:39Z","content":"I have a 3 year old daughter, if this happened to me, my family would be doing exactly the same thing! She deserves to be with her family at this difficult time. Canada should be ashamed of what they are doing.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kyla Horsnall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73550044"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:34:51Z","content":"This is the right thing to do.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ken Andrews","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78239689"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:26:40Z","content":"She has done nothing wrong!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tricia Reed","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/46251728"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:37:50Z","content":"Because it's the right thing to do!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Barb Vessey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31733498"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:16:04Z","content":"This should never happen to a mother.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andrea Lonic","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28626206"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:23:14Z","content":"why is this important? because this shouldnt even be an issue she should be on a plane home. Again just goes to show you that I would never step foot in THAT country. My deepest sympathy to Justine and her family. God Bless and Gods Speed. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"susan  mccaw","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10268475"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:17:23Z","content":"Because I love life","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erick Montesdeoca","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31747780"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:29:22Z","content":"this poor mother needs to go to her sons funeral.  How heartbreaking.  The Cuban govt needs to have a heart!!!!  Shame on them!","like_count":0,"author_name":"kristina dreisbach","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78898822"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:32:37Z","content":"there are no words. My condolences for you terrible loss and the aftermath. Bless","like_count":0,"author_name":"Serene Greene","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51570020"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:53:14Z","content":"If we cannot count on our government to get an innocent women home for her child's funeral how can we believe they serve any of us.\r\nMay your families prayers be answered. You are all in mine.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deborah Barrie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3092559"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:02:18Z","content":"I'm human!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kelly Huthmaker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5357087"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:09:05Z","content":"Justice","like_count":0,"author_name":"Raymond Ford","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34255550"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:26:40Z","content":"It is important as a fellow mother that this mother be allowed to return home to bury her son and receive supports for her family and friends during this time. Secondly being stuck in a foreign country without family and loss of a child this woman must be undergoing undue hardship and emotional distress. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alison Sullivan-Hurley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13218119"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:51:55Z","content":"Why isn't the Canadian govt. helping Canadians in distress around the world?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Douglas Copp","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3288976"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:16:42Z","content":"As a mother of a 3 year old child I cannot imagine having my child die so tragically and then not being able to be present to say goodbye. This poor mother needs to be home to say bye to her son and start to be able to grieve her loss in the presence of friends and family. Stories like these make me never want to travel to a country where the rules are different than Canada.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Lombardo-Seib","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78916154"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T12:25:15Z","content":"Compassion. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda McIntosh","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74809284"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T16:34:50Z","content":"Bring Justine home! No reason a mother should not be able to bury her child. It's way too sad already give her a chance to say goodbye! Bring her home! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Mcarthur","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78728593"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T13:54:12Z","content":"Justine Davis must be released from a Cuban hospital to attend her son' funeral. She has not been charged by the Cuban government. The Canadian Government must demand that she be released and brought home to Canada.\r\nThis is an absolute tragedy and it is imperative that Justine be at her son's funeral Saturday.","like_count":0,"author_name":"jennifer burke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68352558"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:36:10Z","content":"Show a little compassion for this person's huge loss. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joseph Malek","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47137503"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:29:18Z","content":"this lady should not have ot stay there for an accident and should b able to return home to lay her son to rest ot me this is just pathetic that she is being held","like_count":0,"author_name":"melanie caston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22802630"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:35:27Z","content":"Because I am human, a mother, and it is only right that she have the ability to bury her baby by his side.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tanya Riley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78755399"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:42:26Z","content":"It's just too sad. Let her at least say goodbye","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maya Atieh","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70201073"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:14:52Z","content":"Why are we allowing Cuba to hold one of our citizens especially in these tragic circumstances.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bernadette Toner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78872258"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:40:36Z","content":"A Canadian being held against their will in another country is tragic and the Canadian Government needs to be their to help our citizens. What shame that we have to pressure our Government to act to protect & help its people!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Wayne Bertrand","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60512614"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:06:56Z","content":"I am in disbelief this could happen to any one as a fellow citizen of the planet and mother it causes me concern","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erma Gonzalez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31601245"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T05:30:40Z","content":"Sad this girl needs to go home ....","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lorraine Leblanc","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78812175"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:07:04Z","content":"This disgraceful situation should be sorted out \u2013 Canadian officials need to get off their butts!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Keith Dixon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50198143"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:22:38Z","content":"Every mother needs the closure of attending a child's funeral, especially her flesh & blood!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cathy Poupore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51630891"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:26:40Z","content":"tragic","like_count":0,"author_name":"susan cadden","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22000567"}]}{"page":17,"prev_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page=16&page_size=500","next_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page_size=500","total_pages":9,"reasons":[]}{"page":34,"prev_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page=33&page_size=500","next_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page_size=500","total_pages":9,"reasons":[]}{"page":43,"prev_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page=42&page_size=500","next_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page_size=500","total_pages":9,"reasons":[]}{"page":14,"prev_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page=13&page_size=500","next_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page_size=500","total_pages":9,"reasons":[]}{"page":27,"prev_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page=26&page_size=500","next_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page_size=500","total_pages":9,"reasons":[]}{"page":10,"prev_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page=9&page_size=500","next_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page_size=500","total_pages":9,"reasons":[]}{"page":1,"prev_page_endpoint":null,"next_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/1429517/reasons?page=2&page_size=500","total_pages":9,"reasons":[{"created_at":"2014-02-05T16:02:06Z","content":"As a mother who has lost a child I know the importance of being able to say goodbye to your child and having some closure.  If you have a heart pls. let Justine come home and have the closure that she deserves!","like_count":20,"author_name":"Joanne Gentile","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34879066"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T15:21:43Z","content":"No one should have to miss saying their final goodbyes to a loved one, let alone your own child who was lost so traumatically.  Please send this woman home to say goodbye to her son, she will only have that one chance, has she not suffered enough already?","like_count":17,"author_name":"Sabrina Roballo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52714611"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T03:57:37Z","content":"because justine is a good friend of mine and no body deserves to bo detained in a country while the child is being buried in another","like_count":15,"author_name":"hollie staats","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78669135"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:00:19Z","content":"What is the Canadian Embassay there for??  If not to assist Canadians in a time of need. ","like_count":14,"author_name":"Sharon Murphy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66211217"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T15:26:02Z","content":"Because they are my family and I love them and just want her home ","like_count":12,"author_name":"desiree hylton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78718839"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:31:02Z","content":"I actually met Justine and Cameron in Cuba on this vacation. We were on the same plane from Toronto and were at the same resort. The first night my boyfriend and I actually hung out with Justine and Cameron watching the entertainment for the night, exchanged where we were from and about ourselves. Cameron was quite a character at the shows, he was always on the stage dancing and laughing like a little show man. He brought a smile to everyone's face at the resort when he was doing that. The next two days my boyfriend and I would sit with them to watch the show we even hung out by the pool together eating French fries. Cameron was such a bright happy child who deserves to have his mom present at his funeral. \r\n\r\nOnce I heard about the accident the entire resort dedicated the nightly entertainment to him and Justine. Because some of the other travelers saw my boyfriend and I with them so often their thought we knew each other before he vacation. It was such a tragic event and I have been searching for some way to help them.  \r\n\r\nJustine needs to come home to lay her son to rest and Justine needs to continue her recovery here. My condolences goes out to Justine and Cameron's friends and family. Cameron was truly an amazing kid who was so friendly and made everyone smile around him.","like_count":11,"author_name":"Nicole Donaldson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78763135"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:30:16Z","content":"Justine is a \"Mother\" who lost her son in an innocent accident.  She is not in Cuba to start trouble, she just wants to be home to bury her son and say good-bye to  Cameron.  She is no threat to Cuba by leaving to go home. I don't understand Cuba's point on WHY they will not let her go back to Canada. Please allow Justine to go home for the burial of Cameron.  They are an innocent Mother and Son that just wanted to make happy memories on vacation and this terrible, horrific occurrence happened and now CUBA is making it even harder for Justine after her heart is broken.  Cuba is kicking her while she is down and I hope after others see this review that WE WILL STAND UNITED and NOT TAKE A VACATION TO CUBA.  ","like_count":8,"author_name":"Linda Findlay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69457063"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T21:25:03Z","content":"NO mother should have to bury her child but to miss your child's burial is inhuman! ","like_count":7,"author_name":"cinzia tartaglia","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78768973"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T15:14:59Z","content":"The loss of a child is the worst experience a parent could endure. They need to bring her home so she can say her last goodbyes to her son at his funeral. This is just absurd. \n\nPrayers go out to you hun. Hope you can make it home in time. ","like_count":5,"author_name":"Monica Peters","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26686635"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T03:45:26Z","content":"A mother should never have to bury their children and if that happens they need to say goodbye.  From one mother to another we need to get her home.","like_count":5,"author_name":"Shannon Hayman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70332392"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:51:11Z","content":"HAVING  TRAVELLED  FOR 20 years to CUBA ,these  kind of stories have happened so many times before ! . CANADA needs  to help Tourists morein Cuadn situations !--- , I see that Canada  must speak Up NOW!  ----in CUBAI .  I know first hand my own hard times and so many others with the rigid rules of Cuban communism. Step In NOW CANADA !  I  know this! -- the rigths of Candains ARE NOT  ! being honoured in CUBA . in this story and so many others . REV.  SARAH\r\n BUNNETT-GIBSON ","like_count":4,"author_name":"Sarah Bunnett-Gibson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66455549"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:29:28Z","content":"What if it were my family or your family ? Its just morally right and I almost feel embarrassed our country is not doing more to help in this tragic situation.","like_count":4,"author_name":"Jason Donnelly","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78856379"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:25:59Z","content":"Ok, I am not one to spread this type of thing around facebook, but if signing this helps it is only a signature.  What the hell is wrong with our government?  Can send billions in aid to other countries, but can't send aid to a taxpayer?  I call Bullshit! ","like_count":4,"author_name":"Monica Partridge","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72228344"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:30:33Z","content":"As a mother who also lost a child I too know of the importance of being able to say goodbye to your child and having some closure is IMPORTANT! Lord, I bring before you today to please place your hands on ALL parties involved to bring Justine Davis home so she can bury her three-year-old son. Cameron,you are now with the angels may you R.I.P.\r\n","like_count":4,"author_name":"Rosanna Ganhao","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56949795"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T13:19:21Z","content":"Justice and human decency.","like_count":3,"author_name":"Kyle Verwey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78706023"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:40:12Z","content":"The 30 day after an accident stay in cuba is up, time to let this women come home and bury her son. May god bless you Cameron.","like_count":3,"author_name":"Cynthia S","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75498737"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:36:40Z","content":"FAMILY is the most important thing we got!!!! Dont taker hers away without saying goodbye","like_count":3,"author_name":"Chrissy Da Silva","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78878877"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:57:26Z","content":"Human decency matters. Unless there are other criminal charges against Justine, there does not appear to be any logic to her detention. Surely the Canadian ambassador can intervene today to have Justine home for Saturday. ","like_count":3,"author_name":"Rebecca Ward","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24584210"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:27:23Z","content":"It was an accident. A mother needs to be at her son's funeral. She must be devastated enough so she needs to come home. I travel to Cuba a lot and this will make me think things differently and not travel there. ","like_count":3,"author_name":"Annette McCann","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57452655"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:36:52Z","content":"As a Canadian I am ashamed our government isn't doing more to help canadians abroad.","like_count":3,"author_name":"Deborah Maloney-Mccaig","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33835835"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:28:30Z","content":"A mother needs to be there for her child regardless of out of country laws. I really hope she is able to come home to her family and be supported during this tragic time.","like_count":3,"author_name":"Jenn Waghorn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/54373613"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:25:46Z","content":"This situation makes no sense at all. Why on earth would not Canadian officials do the right thing immediately? Do it!!","like_count":3,"author_name":"Morley Chalmers","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77907373"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T13:13:09Z","content":"Help get Justine Davis home from Cuba!","like_count":3,"author_name":"Rorie Digout","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78705495"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:26:28Z","content":"This is a human rights issue not a MVA investigation. Justine is being treated as a criminal and she should be released to mourn the loss of her child and set free. If this happened to a cuban tourist we would treat her/him like a golden saint and give them top notch care and provide everything we could to make the situation comfortable as possible. Cuba is dropping the ball and failing at an opportunity to look positive in a global light","like_count":3,"author_name":"dean landry","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60709858"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:02:45Z","content":"she has the right to be at her sons funeral!","like_count":2,"author_name":"Jen Hart","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57463314"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:02:49Z","content":"please allow this poor mother to lay her baby to rest. Just think of your children, grandchildren, cousins, aunt, uncle anyone yoy love dearly not being able to be there to lay them to rest pkease have a heart and sign this. You can make a difference to a mother in need of her lil angel being gone too soon. In loving memory of lil Cameron &lt;3 ","like_count":2,"author_name":"naomi dorantes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78866421"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:35:50Z","content":"Ambassador, it is only what I would expect from my Government should such a tragedy befall me or any of my family. Surely, a situation such as this merits intervention beyond \"typical\" diplomatic avenues.","like_count":2,"author_name":"paul steers","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/55974476"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:47:46Z","content":"One of the responsibilities of Canadian Ambassadors is to look out for Canadians experiencing difficulty in foreign countries.  It appears this has not happened, so far, to the degree needed in this particular case.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Paul Olynek","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60467193"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:56:22Z","content":"Important to be with her son as he is laid to rest and to say her final good-byes.  Noone should have to ever go through the pain of losing their own child but also to not be at his funeral is not right.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Sally Louie-Honch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76228030"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:56:24Z","content":"It's one thing for this poor mother to have to bury her child, but to potentially miss the funeral is just wrong. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Kristy Voetberg","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78866132"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:47:50Z","content":"Canadians need to be given the benefit of doubt.  It's a funeral, for her son!!  This is discusting that the Cuban Government is allowed to do this.  Justine needs to be a part of putting her handsome son to rest.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Kim Pollock","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63569376"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:56:34Z","content":"I am a traveller of as of the past year and it concerns me that the government seems to turn it back when its citizens are in trouble.  I have never been to Cuba and one day I intend to visit, but stories such as this can easily and unreasonably persuade one not to.  Is the Government proud to have people fearful of exploring the world freely???   I want to be able to feel comfort and security when travelling and I think with all the effort that one must put in to leave the country & return (ie.passports and related costs, flight costs and lengthy airport waits and procedures), that we deserve that!  Please don't abandon this family or anyone else!","like_count":2,"author_name":"Tanya Wagner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73819678"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:36:29Z","content":"I wish more people understood the dangers of travelling to foreign countries. This is not the first time this has happened in Cuba. It is tragic that a mother should have such a terrible accident, lose a child, be detained and then not be able to properly grieve the loss. Yves Gagnon deserves to have the Canadian Government come to her aid and end this horrible nightmare.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Dolly Israel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59798032"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:47:58Z","content":"there should be absolutely no reason as to why this mother cannot be at her son's funeral","like_count":2,"author_name":"Heidi Colombo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62996676"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:47:59Z","content":"Stephen Harper's administration should be heavily pressured to act on this. To ignore it is reprehensible","like_count":2,"author_name":"Robert Young","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66721568"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:36:33Z","content":"In support of Justine allow her to Leave Cuba there is no reason she needs to be there. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Colleen Porter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27074769"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:49:57Z","content":"Because she is Canadaian and needs to be able to be at her son's funeral! let her leave now! she has already been through enough! this is cruel and unusual punishment! Put her on the plane home! have a heart! ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Jenn Duvivier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78865822"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:48:15Z","content":"I cannot understand why our government is unable to assist a Canadian citizen.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Susan Fehrman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47203483"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:03:46Z","content":"My son was harassed on the way into Cuba 2 years ago, they said he had marijuana and interrogated him for 4 hours. They asked if he had smoked cocaine the previous year. He had not been there since he was 10, 17 years before. So a $150 fine ( For what) and a $50 taxi ride later. I tried to get the cuban embassey to reimburse him nothing..and The Canadian Extgernal affaisrt would not lift a finger, no more cuba for me  after almost 30 years of visiting. I doubt External affairs will lifet a finger here ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Dr Michael  Last NamePilon ( Major Retired","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30033069"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:50:06Z","content":"The most worst thing in the world is to have to bury your child, the mother must and needs to be there...I feel her pain!","like_count":2,"author_name":"Connie McKinnon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47071072"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:57:03Z","content":"This is not a human behavior !!! This is Horrible !!!","like_count":2,"author_name":"Edgar Santos","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71451934"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:50:42Z","content":"This young mother needs to be with her son when he is laid to rest. Please give this mother and son peace.  Sending thoughts and prayers to the family. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Georgina Tziavaras","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78865864"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:04:46Z","content":"seems like a no brainier -why would anyone not support this?","like_count":2,"author_name":"Robert Gindli","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52077179"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:04:50Z","content":"This is very important to me. She has Human Rights and should not be held in a country that she has done nothing wrong.  If she needs to get home to attend her sons funeral. I do understant Cuba wants her to stay until the trial, but sometime compassion is the best policy.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Brenda Swarts","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78866495"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:58:01Z","content":"This seems fairly simple and obvious to me. Get off your bureaucratic asses, gov't of Canada, and get this grieving mother home! It was no problem getting home 40,000 \"Canadians\" from the middle east a few years back when there was increasing turmoil in that region, that expensive undertaking happened pretty quickly; why foot-drag on getting this Canadian vacationer home? Shame on Canada AND Cuba! Let's all encourage Canadians to spend their tourist dollars anywhere BUT Cuba!!","like_count":2,"author_name":"Leslie Rose","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72107210"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:49:43Z","content":"This is a real shame for anyone to suffer. Canada should do more to help bring Justine home.","like_count":2,"author_name":"James Best","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36091823"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:49:53Z","content":"Nothing is more important than to allow a mother to bury her own child. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Tere Lopez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26834623"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:59:16Z","content":"As a mother, I can only imagine how devastated Justine Davis is over the death of her son and not being able to attend his funeral.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Alison Slack","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36822262"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:52:19Z","content":"It breaks my heart.\r\n\r\nNo one should have to suffer like this. Let her come home.\r\n\r\nGive her this small comfort in her tragedy.","like_count":2,"author_name":"joann field","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16430388"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:33:49Z","content":"This could happen to anyone.  If the Canadian government is not willing to help in times like these, then I'm ashamed to be a Canadian.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Paula Hughson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/49344279"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:33:11Z","content":"We are Canadians not animals..","like_count":2,"author_name":"Sandra Mcleod , Rainy Creek Ranch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78336324"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:50:36Z","content":"Because it's the right thing to do, this is her son, is there really a need for an explination?","like_count":2,"author_name":"chris poulin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17081433"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:50:39Z","content":"Dude, her kid died for fuck's sake","like_count":2,"author_name":"Malcolm Latreille","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63183385"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:34:08Z","content":"Hasn't this poor woman been through enough already? Let her come home to grieve and recover with friends and family, not alone in a foreign country.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Lyne Gougeon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/64701689"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:34:10Z","content":"Please think how you would feel if you were her. Please do the right thing so she can come home for her son's Cameron's funeral.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Jenny Take","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63550974"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:30:00Z","content":"No parent should lose a child, let alone not being able to say their final goodbye. My deepest sympathy to the family. :-(","like_count":2,"author_name":"Jean-Claude Boucher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44686201"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:55:30Z","content":"I know that when we are travelling abroad we are basically on our own and there's not much that the government can do to help, but please pull out all the stops to do what you can for this poor mother.  This is heart breaking.  ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Pauline MacLeod Farley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9694910"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:35:28Z","content":"No mother should be held back from attending her own sons funeral. Everyone should be entitled to grieve properly.","like_count":2,"author_name":"heather hermiston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66848907"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:35:31Z","content":"Sadly, our Prime Minister, most of his cabinet and half of his MPs call themselves \"Christian.\"  If this were true, they would do something about this and bring Justine home.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Thomas Corbett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11851688"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:55:42Z","content":"she belongs in canada!!! has she not been through enough???? ","like_count":2,"author_name":"melanie price","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78866093"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:52:39Z","content":"She was in an accident. There was no criminal intent. The only reason our government will not help our citizens is that it might upset the Americans if we have direct communication. For her to be left with out help due to the wounded pride of. Another country is simply wrong, it is betrayal.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Gerald Himmelspach","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10937224"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:38:40Z","content":"It is a tragedy to detain this woman  for any reason...she is not a criminal...she is an injured and grieving mother.  The Cuban government should be ashamed of itself.","like_count":1,"author_name":"stephanie talbot","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78882134"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:03:03Z","content":"The mother of a child needs to be at her son's funeral It is so sad he has died while she was away LORD HELP HER GET HOME TO HER SON ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Laurie  Lindsay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27457910"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:58:10Z","content":"I tcertainly makes me thinK twIce about ever going to Cuba as a tourist.  Actually I will not spend a penny until this mother rs returned to Canada.What is wrong with the Canadian government that THEY CANNOT DO ANYTHING TO HELP THIS MOTHER AND HER FAMILY. \r\n","like_count":1,"author_name":"Elizabeth Stefan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77389765"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:03:05Z","content":"I'm a mom and would need to be there.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Nicole Brickell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78884086"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:29:55Z","content":"Have some sympathy, no reason to keep this innocent mother in Cuba. Release her to her home in Canada and allow her to put her son to rest and better yet morn with her family! ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Stacey Graham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78881564"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:49:44Z","content":"Unless they have charges against her, then she should be allowed to leave.  She needs closure and attending her sons funeral is important, and she's a Canadian citizen, and Cuba has  maintained good relations with Canada re: tourist industry.  Is there anything else involved.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Doreen Roy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/55606247"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:59:59Z","content":"I am so sorry for your loss and for the terrible circumstances that lead to Cameron's death, and that now continue. I hope that on humanitarian grounds alone the Canadian government will attempt to do more to remedy this awful situation, which is a tragedy but not a crime.  And the Cuban government should take note that future Canadian tourists may think twice before booking their trip if they are unwilling to be reasonable in situations like this. I know that Cuba is now off my list for a last-minute get-away; it can't possible be worth the risk.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Amanda O'Connor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15068747"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:34:18Z","content":"I hope everybody remembers NOT not to vote conservative in the next election! Their foreign policy is just making things worse for Canadians.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lee Elson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60951157"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:12:34Z","content":"Cette jeune femme et son fils ont \u00e9t\u00e9 victimes d'un accident, qu'attendez-vous pour la lib\u00e9rer? Quelle est la raison d'\u00eatre d'une ambassade, on paie vos salaires et d\u00e9penses en tant que contribuables canadiens, vous existez pour qui? ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Idelta Vieira","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60923283"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:10:50Z","content":"As a mother, my heart goes out to Justine and her husband. As a Canadian, I am ashamed at the lack of push on the part of our government. As a traveller with children, Cuba can consider itself off my list of destinations.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kelley Wilson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71385157"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:58:31Z","content":"Being held against fee will, even though there aren't any charges laid or mal-intent, is a Canadian Human rights violation. Our government has a duty to protect our rights. This is down right shameful.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Clayton Hassell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66141619"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:06:17Z","content":"This entire situation is tragic enough.  But to not allow the Mother to attend her only young child's funeral makes this beyond tragic.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Brenda Hurley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38125255"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:34:27Z","content":"It looks as if the Canadian Embassy has been and still is  less than useful in this situation and that somebody in Cuba is trying to make extra dollars (is the $9500 for Cuba, for transportation fees or what?) for a matter which is in no way criminal. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Camille Legare","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20758801"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:09:16Z","content":"This woman is locked up because of an accident.  She was on a scooter and it was her son who was killed.  Where is the justice in that Cuba?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Natalie Murray","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39718653"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:52:50Z","content":"She needs closure.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Gwen Spencer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65652636"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:30:05Z","content":"Justine needs to be around her family at this difficult time and should be home.  She has suffered enough!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"dennise minhinnick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30090817"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:03:13Z","content":"I have a toddler...","like_count":1,"author_name":"H\u00e9l\u00e8ne Marceau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/46976685"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:49:57Z","content":"Humanitarian reasons!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Ron Faithfull","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77037266"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:49:59Z","content":"I too am a Mother who has had two of my children pass away. Fortunately I was there for their funerals. May God speed this Mother home to bury her son.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Ann Kinney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44795410"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:53:00Z","content":"It is sad enough that she lost her son. Help her.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Ron Porteous","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11242210"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:05:07Z","content":"I HATE INJUSTICE ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Daniel Boisjoly","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44834552"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:16:05Z","content":"This is important to me because I am a mother and a grandmother. Too bad men can't feel that kind of bond with their children, or do they?\r\n","like_count":1,"author_name":"Emily  Kierstead","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24601463"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:53:51Z","content":"Unless she is being kept because they believe there is foul play involved in this, why isnt she being allowed to leave?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Heather Bennett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44523677"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:12:49Z","content":"Mothers should be able to see their babies one last time","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jessie Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59867790"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:46:35Z","content":"The elementary human decency.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lucie Hamel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72948418"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:09:24Z","content":"As sad as it is, every mother should have the right to be at her own child's funeral. Canadian Embassy STOP being so HEARTLESS !!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Hope Hedrick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5244786"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:11:05Z","content":"It is already a tragedy in itself that a mother lost her child, at least grant 