e Canadian Embassy has not helped in this matter","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kelly Creyke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37922541"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:46:46Z","content":"She's in need of us Canadians...go get her and bring her back home safely and in time.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Leo Lefebvre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47128599"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:06:34Z","content":"Ridiculous considering Canada's long term relationship with Cuba - not acceptable!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Paulette Leveris","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56884088"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:17:45Z","content":"This mother needs too be home in her country and more importantly she needs to be able too attend her son's funeral, Cameron is now with his grandpa, Hope she is able too come home.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Del Palmisano","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61948642"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:50:14Z","content":"I share the same feelings","like_count":1,"author_name":"Muazzam Orakzai","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24264851"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:13:01Z","content":"We pay the Harper government to provide these embassy and consular services.  Do your jobs or vacate the offices","like_count":1,"author_name":"Geoff  Cassino","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12690052"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:50:16Z","content":"I'd like to know what Canada's ambassador in Cuba, Yves Gagnon, has been doing to assist this Canadian in distress.  ISN'T THAT HIS JOB?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Mary Pal","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20609848"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:23:58Z","content":"This mother has been through a devastating accident and needs to be allowed to come home to Canada so she can attend her beautiful son's funeral. God Bless!","like_count":1,"author_name":"jan gordon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16816193"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:09:37Z","content":"Its an injustice that needs to be addressed\r\n","like_count":1,"author_name":"sean bourke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28911474"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:06:39Z","content":"This poor mother needs to be there to put her darling to rest in the right way and she needs the support of her family and friends to get thu this very difficult time.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Brenda Pedersen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9186290"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:42:57Z","content":"Please do the right thing","like_count":1,"author_name":"Dave Abbey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8435690"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:19:11Z","content":"I understand that the laws of the country that something happens in need to be respected.  I also understand that the Canadian government can not force its values on another country, however in this case no harm seems to have been done to another party and if their was damage to the truck involved in the accident the Davis family would, I assume, pay for it.  So there is no reason for further detaining Justine Davis unless the authorities have reasonable doubt that it was an accident.  So please let Ms. Davis go home to grieve with her family and start a hopefully better part of her life.  Thank you.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Armin Arend","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15468771"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:05:50Z","content":"Let her go home to her son's funeral","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kathy Crawford","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58263567"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:57:23Z","content":"I am a mother.  Cannot imagine ever losing a child let alone not being to attend their funeral.  Heartbreaking.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Sarah Lacasse","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31588626"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:13:09Z","content":"This is horrible - hard enough to lose a child but to not be allowed out of the Country to get home for his funeral ? No parent should have to go through this.","like_count":1,"author_name":"heather pratt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34412529"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:59:38Z","content":"A Mother needs to be at her own Childs Funeral !!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Barbara Marchildon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72036835"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:39:14Z","content":"That is terrible and devastating to the mother .Why is the mother being held is she not a Canadian and where is our government .They help educate and give free to forieners and noting to protect a Canadian disappointed in our Government over this ","like_count":1,"author_name":"michelle lavictoire","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75268126"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:24:15Z","content":"Because I am a mother and a Canadian! She has suffered enough at the lost of her son and should rightfully be there for his funeral. No parent should bury their child before themselves. My heart goes out to the whole family. Bring Justine home!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Cindy Winters","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78881306"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:39:16Z","content":"Canada needs to build a better Relationship with Foreign Country's starting with Cuba","like_count":1,"author_name":"Bruce Custer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72340828"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:54:15Z","content":"This kind of bureaucratic obstruction is excessive and unnecessary. It could easily be resolved by more compassion and some diplomatic efforts. Canada is a lucrative economic contributor to Cuba's economy while health costs in Cuba are far from exploitive. These alone are grounds for negotiation and a swift resolution.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Michel Casselman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/19783243"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:06:00Z","content":"This is so sad and tragic. PLease help this lady reunite with her son one last time.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Sophie Marier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/19809239"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:11:45Z","content":"Please make it possible for this innocent grieving woman to attend her son's funeral.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Danielle Bobker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60110757"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:47:07Z","content":"I am a mom and she needs to be home for closure","like_count":1,"author_name":"vickie hennig","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78882782"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:11:49Z","content":"I cannot begin to imagine the pain Justine is going through, she should be at home getting comforted by family and friends, not detained.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Melanie Posthuma","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69862462"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:43:12Z","content":"Canadian Embassy in Cuba sounds pretty pathetic. STOP PAPER PUSHING, START DOING YOUR JOB","like_count":1,"author_name":"R P","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44893528"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:03:51Z","content":"For humanitarian reasons","like_count":1,"author_name":"Catherine Parker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30276725"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:16:29Z","content":"I believe that one of the paramount jobs of our federal government is to support our citizens abroad.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Patricia  Macdougall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2653386"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:53:47Z","content":"I can't even imagine what Justine must be going through. This is not right.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Danielle Williams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16446346"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:16:30Z","content":"please just help her get home","like_count":1,"author_name":"Donna Le Blanc","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78885272"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:00:53Z","content":"A mother deserves her right to attend her child's funeral. So tragic and sad, I can't imagine what she's going through. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Thatsany Khamsingsavath","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78883868"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:06:10Z","content":"It's an embassy's basic duty to help citizens abroad. We pay you for this. Do your job.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Julien Hardy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11866884"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:50:34Z","content":"There's nothing as important as a mothers love...and it's just common sense that she should!!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"patty munden","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71121011"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:54:25Z","content":"No mother should ever have to bury her child and to not be there for the service would be unimaginable.  Have a heart, let her come home.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kim Carvery","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71804691"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:07:05Z","content":"This is just so wrong! And if Cuba's driving laws don't change, perhaps we should stop visiting :(\r\n","like_count":1,"author_name":"Penny Hall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32113178"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:00:55Z","content":"Please allow this mother to bury her child.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Mari Knox","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63312033"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:35:29Z","content":"She needs family close by. What a tragedy.....a lost blessing. My condolences. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Christian Ying","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8075465"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:18:44Z","content":"she needs to be there for the funeral and with family","like_count":1,"author_name":"Dara Ross","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74125396"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:47:15Z","content":"No mother should be put through this anguish on top of what has already happened, this is outrageous.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Sandra Cole","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78882795"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:47:15Z","content":"I care about this case because I believe the mother is not guilty of any crime. I will expect the Canadian Embassy to be involved in releasing this young mother. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Tiuley Alguindigue","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52303242"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:19:28Z","content":"This poor mom needs all the help she can get! If anyone has a spare minute, plz sign the petition to put the pressure on the Gov't of Canada and let them know we're watching!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Ashley Veniott","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/42315875"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:12:11Z","content":"It is a mother's right to  be able to attend her child's funeral.Iris Brunning","like_count":1,"author_name":"Iris Brunning","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60011964"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:12:11Z","content":"SOUNDZ RATHER STRANGE SHE IS BEING HELD UP-IS SHE CHARGED WITH ANYTHING?-IF NOT IT IS LUDICROUS THAT SHE CAN'T RETURN-IS THERE ANY REASON SHE IS BEING HELD AGAINST HER WILL?MONEY IS GENERALLY AN ISSUE IN THESE CASES AND MAYB SOME ONE NEEDS TO B PAID OFF TO GET THIS BALL ROLLING!THERE SEEMS 2 B AN UNDERLYING PROBLEM SOME ONE MAYB UNAWARE OF!IF SO-LET HER ATTEND THE FUNERAL AND THEN RETURN-THERE IS THIS HUMAN THING CALLED COMPASSION THAT IS BCOMING MORE ELUSIVE AS TIME GOES ON!-PEOPLE ONLY CARE IF U SHOW THEM THE MONEY!-SAD BUT TRUE!","like_count":1,"author_name":"garth morgan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47227815"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:07:07Z","content":"So unfair that a loving mother suffers from the lost of her beloved son but that she is punish to attend funeral. Furthermore, Cuban political regim is a dictatorial one that can not be trusted. Most Cuban women have to prostitute themselves in order to eat. I was there 2 years ago for 2 weeks and I will never go back until the regime changes.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Colette Ob","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61238778"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:12:14Z","content":"It is important for the grieving mother to say goodbye to her child. nnv","like_count":1,"author_name":"Nancy Vichert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72758212"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:03:56Z","content":"Her Universal Human Rights are being totally ignored by our own government....shame","like_count":1,"author_name":"Michel Coia","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78884184"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:54:05Z","content":"How do they have the right to keep a mom from her dead son.. Because of an accident in their own country?  Canadian government should stop support of all unnecessary travel cuba ... their #1 economic survivor . . go big or stay home...","like_count":1,"author_name":"lm fanet","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78879800"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:57:39Z","content":"I am a mother and this could have easily happened to me.  I am ashamed that our Canadian government isn't serving it's citizens abroad.  This woman has been a victim of unfortunate circumstances and the  embassy officials in cuba, particulary Yves Gagnon, should be working day and night to get her back to Canada.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Catherine Woods","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35660267"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:07:10Z","content":"this not a time for buorocratic red tape and passing the buck - allowing a mother to bury her child is humanitarian.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Cindy Devine","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8254193"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:31:23Z","content":"Please our Ambassador. Please help free Justine Davis so she can come home to Canada for her son's funeral this Saturday. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Mohammad Ali Malik","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50355683"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:35:41Z","content":"No one ever knows when tragedy strikes, and we should always do what we can to support those involved. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Erin Tiesma","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/49431550"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:25:05Z","content":"because we want the government to act on all of our behalves when we need it. if they have to be pressured into it - that is pitiful - but i want to pressure because it is the only thing they respond to.","like_count":1,"author_name":"judi tetro","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60995085"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:10:07Z","content":"This mother should be allowed to put her son to rest and released from Cuba!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Shannon Billings","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66337348"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:48:56Z","content":"Could very well be one of my family member can happen to anyone","like_count":1,"author_name":"Leo Arbour","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44707916"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:43:26Z","content":"Please have compassion and allow Justine to be at her sons' funeral.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Sandra Campbell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17202529"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:16:44Z","content":"In view of this tragic story, my wife and I have opted not to consider Cuba as a vacation destination this year (much to her regret). Money talks...even in Cuba.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Denis Lavictoire","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43867402"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:39:33Z","content":"The fundamental right of a parent to be at the burial of their child when there is no criminal record to present that. It is disgraceful that our own government should take such a hands-off approach to this woman's pain.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Michael Wiley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21180485"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:00:27Z","content":"To help Justine (who my heart goes out to) but also to impress upon our government that they need to 'clean up their act' when it comes to helping Canadians in distress overseas. . . it is far too frequent a story","like_count":1,"author_name":"Harold (Hal) Holt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34953834"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:47:31Z","content":"Simple human dignity.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Matthew Teal","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22492464"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:51:09Z","content":"Justine is a cousin, I can not imagine how she is feeling being a mother too \r\n","like_count":1,"author_name":"Katherine Monteith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26900689"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:25:15Z","content":"This is a tragic story with a twist so horrific, it is impossible to understand. Please help this poor woman who has lost everything.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Carolyn Rasiuk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35709823"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:31:31Z","content":"This petition should be obvious to anyone.  Justine should be helped to get back here.  Thanks","like_count":1,"author_name":"Manuel Robert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7114678"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:43:33Z","content":"I find it very worrisome to think that my country would not go to bat for me in the event of a catastrophic situation in a foreign country. The loss of a child is devastating. Justine will never recover from the emotional trauma and must also cope with her own injuries. I can't imagine not being able to attend my child's funeral on top of that. Sun seekers should think twice about purchasing cheap Cuban holidays. And, our government needs to step up and help get her home.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Elizabeth Edwards","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/55472873"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:35:57Z","content":"She lost her son.  She deserves to be here for the funeral. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Vicki Goodwin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78881958"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:10:15Z","content":"Heartbreaking for ANY mother to not be present at her own sons funeral.\r\nHave some compassion Cuba","like_count":1,"author_name":"Sarah Taylor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52750418"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:19:19Z","content":"Please do whatever you can to help get this mother home to her  child so she can say goodbye!   Why is she being treated as if she is a criminal in all of this!   \r\n Are the damages to the truck so extensive that she is bring held for this reason?  If she is not charged with anything, she should be free to leave the country!  Canadian Government - can you not do something? Too many people are being left in countries to fight for themselves.  Step up and do your jobs!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Sandy Scotchmer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37909641"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:04:08Z","content":"My heart goes out to Justine and her family. It is really upsetting to know that she's lost her little baby and even more so that she cannot come to her own child's funeral. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"kate vinokurov","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65978622"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:43:34Z","content":"No moral sense in keeping a mother away, from her family let her grieve this unimaginable death with her loved ones!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Marusca Guerriero","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78879212"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:12:46Z","content":"We shouldn't have to even explain why!  It's ridiculous to keep a mother from her own son's funeral and ridiculous to keep her there because of what was obviously an accident.  Let this woman come home!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jami Bruneau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68422448"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:36:04Z","content":"Like many Canadians, I have begun to tire utterly of the Harper regime's treatment of any Canadian who is not a corporate executive or shareholder. I suggest that they begin to do their job of serving the Canadian people if they wish to have any hope of being elected for any reason other than a divided opposition.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Stephen Langevin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23975994"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:43:37Z","content":"No one should miss the opportunity to say their last goodbye to a loved one, especially that of your child.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Margot Biesinger","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77500528"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:00:48Z","content":"Please let her salute her child one last time. It was all an accident.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Carole Proulx","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25290859"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:31:41Z","content":"This mom has enough pain but the pain of a little child being buried without his mom present due to Gov. ignorance is not acceptable\r\n","like_count":1,"author_name":"Doris Grant","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41866967"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:16:55Z","content":"she needs to be with her baby","like_count":1,"author_name":"yvette mccarthy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/42400460"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:43:41Z","content":"A mom should be present at her child's funeral. As the only death was the child, only serious injuries to the mother; it begs the question of why Cuban officials are dragging this out. I expect better than this from our Canadian government... but have learned  unless we hod them to a fire they could care less: not happening to their family...","like_count":1,"author_name":"claire romm","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12754551"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:43:41Z","content":"Why is this important to me you ask? Because this situation is wrong on so many levels!  Canadians should help Canadians  and mothers should attend their child funeral! Please sign and pass this on to help our Canadian Ambassador to Cuba free Justine Davis! Together we can make a difference!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Colleen Taylor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38661106"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:00:56Z","content":"It is very unfortunate that Canadian abroad get so little assistance from our own Government, shame on them!  I Travel quite a bit myself, fortunately I have never needed assistance from Foreign Affairs or our Embassy but one never knows. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Andre Corkum","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32170727"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:47:46Z","content":"I am heartbroken.\r\nDon't know what to say. People please support Justine!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Iva Georgieva","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/53595580"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:04:20Z","content":"I believe in Justice and Canada's role in these countries is non-effective.  We need to truly represent Canadians if we sign on as Ambassadors to a given country; otherwise, it's a mockery.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Yvonne Myers","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/46936312"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:19:35Z","content":"Canadian citizens involved in incidents abroad should receive the maximum assistance possible from their government in such cases. The Crown has the moral duty to go to bat for its citizens both at home and abroad.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Peter Stuart","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72960335"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:47:46Z","content":"The mom should be there to his own son funeral.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Doerte Schulze","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78882833"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:54:56Z","content":"This situation ,witch seems not treetabla my normal travel agent or insurance company most then be assumed by the Goverment of Canada .\r\nJustin Davis is a victim and not a criminel. So give her all the help that this creeving mother's intitle to.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jean-Marc De Nobile","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75976565"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:43:49Z","content":"A mother need to be to the her son funerals. I'm not surprise of that lot of tourists doesnt know that it's very dangerous to rent a car or a scooter in Cuba even with their insurances. You have to pay for all damages even in private in public places.  I sent my best regards and my condoleances to the family.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Nancy Asselin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60558605"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:43:46Z","content":"I am a mother of 2 and just the thought of having to bury her child is devastating but not being allowed to say good-bye and get closure is inhumane.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Elyse  Belinski","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24538406"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:36:14Z","content":"Canadians need to know the risks of travelling to such countries with unknown laws.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Russell Watson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63857069"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:19:40Z","content":"i have lost two young sons on tragic situations and I would be devastated if I were not able to attend their funerals","like_count":1,"author_name":"joel bollers","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78881071"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:01:12Z","content":"It makes me realize two things:\r\n1) that Cuba should not be a holiday destination for my family\r\n2) and that once again the Canadian Government's behaviour is an embarrassment for Canadians.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Ian MacCallum","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16391325"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:47:48Z","content":"No mother should have to suffer like this. she probably blames herself every day. Let her put her baby to rest let her go home.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Angela Castle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35203849"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:01:12Z","content":"This is not right and Justine should be allowed out of Cuba, especially to attend Cameron's funeral","like_count":1,"author_name":"Rena Younge","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33735051"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:13:07Z","content":"Because this situation is totally unacceptable. How come I'm not surprised, though.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Mich\u00e8le Fairfield","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6591329"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:32:02Z","content":"Please help this Canadian mother say good bye to her son!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Mark Nicoll","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51011571"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:04:26Z","content":"tragic and probably full of miscommunications and bureaucracy ...shouldn't have to happen. very sad","like_count":1,"author_name":"leon levin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15868308"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:07:12Z","content":"I believe our government is so involved with themselves, they forgot while they are there. It's time for Canadians to start speaking up and standing up for ourrights. Canadians are suffering from their neglect. I have been a conservative since 1956, and have now lost faith in their policies. Its time for government to start doing their job and protect us, the voters. Citizens should do as I am now about to do and notify my minister of parliament of my change in support.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Bruce Russell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59836634"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:26:04Z","content":"Mercy needs to be part of the equation. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Debbie Quarrington","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/67271601"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:07:40Z","content":"Les fronti\u00e8res ne devraient pas emp\u00eacher le mouvement des personnes. Je me mets \u00e0 la place de la pauvre maman. Je suis scandalis\u00e9.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Louis Casgrain","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60118313"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:44:05Z","content":"It is inhumane to prevent a mother from attending her child's funeral because of beaurocracy.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Deborah Parliament","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60907964"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:07:14Z","content":"It is rediculous to hold someone in custody over a car accident like this one.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Joan Williams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57465740"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:07:42Z","content":"It should be important to every civilized person! I realize the world is only politically correct now and not civilized. Bring this girl home where she cam mourn her dead child and be with her family. This world makes me sick!\r\n","like_count":1,"author_name":"Michael Durocher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78884506"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:20:04Z","content":"I thought Cuba and Canada had close ties????","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lily Caravella","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9442833"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:32:07Z","content":"This situation is unbearable and Cuba must be forced to allow Justine to leave. This can greatly impact on Cuba's much needed tourism industry!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Rob Eastwood","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50671077"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:26:17Z","content":"There is little details posted by the cuban government on this issue . Either charge her with something or let her go back to her family to mourn her son.  \r\n ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lillian Mcgovern","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78881402"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:44:13Z","content":"Why wouldn't it be important to every parent?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Donald Osbourne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47988467"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:49:53Z","content":"Why is important to me? its because i am a Mother of two little girls!! ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Cinmei Breton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78879540"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:40:07Z","content":"A mother should be able to bury her son, at the very least. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Wasim Khan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48426440"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:20:08Z","content":"I see know reason why Justine is being detained and therefore no reason for the Canadian government to step forward and get her home!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Deborah Nason","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26986685"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:36:35Z","content":"A mother should be with her son to grieve the loss.  I cannot imagine how horrible it would be not to be at his funeral.  It would haunt the poor woman the rest of her life.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jan Willis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69764807"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:04:34Z","content":"Compassion","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jason Watkin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57712807"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:01:33Z","content":"Develope compassion...","like_count":1,"author_name":"martin bell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62883970"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:36:35Z","content":"This is important to me because I will NOT travel to any country as a tourist that is this corrupt or stupid.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Laura Cyr","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31512567"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:44:04Z","content":"It is tragic not only that this young woman has lost her beautiful child, but that she is being detained in the country in which it happened. Why can the Canadian embassy not intervene? Is it because of Canadian diplomatic policy, or Cuban policy?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Claire Rannie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/46702153"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:44:04Z","content":"Because this is such a sad story, and she should be allowed to come home. My heart just brakes for her.","like_count":1,"author_name":"jean lockett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73840744"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:58:18Z","content":"People shouldn't suffer like that. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Larry Morris","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63453019"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:17:15Z","content":"This mother should be close to her family during this tramatic time in her life.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Karen Fischer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16932521"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:26:35Z","content":"It is already devastating enough that she lost her son. There is no reason why she should have to miss his funeral.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Gale McCauley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62553971"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:13:46Z","content":"ohhh how sad..my prayers go out to you all..id be honoured to sign this...god bless","like_count":1,"author_name":"Pauline Bradley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62311547"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:13:50Z","content":"She needs to be there to put her son to rest. My heart hurts so bad for her.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Danielle Wieteska","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30443230"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:50:13Z","content":"If there are not going to be any criminal charges laid then let the poor woman come home to bury her child!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Heather Brooks","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7607963"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:58:25Z","content":"A mother should be able to bury her baby and Cuuba should let her go. Very sad situation.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Patricia McAlear","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60585895"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:20:35Z","content":"I want to see the Canadian Embassy change the way they help Canadians abroad! My husband and I were left stranded in Central America in 2005 by the Cdn Embassy. They were not helpful at all and we were left to fend for ourselves. Ironically enough it was an employee from the Swiss Embassy that helped us out in the end!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Natalia Toews","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12987527"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:07:54Z","content":"I am a mother of two young boys and words cannot describe how I feel about this situation. What a horrendous story. Please bring this woman home...rest in peace little one!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jessie Theriault","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78284057"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:01:44Z","content":"As a mother, I can't imagine losing a child, let alone not be able to attend their funeral. My heart aches for this mother, all alone at a time like this, instead of being with her son and family.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Miranda McCaig","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78883957"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:36:52Z","content":"I feel that if Justine was from thr Province of Quebec a lot more effort would have been used to have her home in Canada by now. The Ambassador should be recalled and at the same time replaced. A very sad situation. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"MICHAEL A HOOPER","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63529352"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:14:04Z","content":"I can't imagine the anguish this young mum is going through and don't understand why our government aren't doing everything they can to get her home to Canada. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lorraine  Moore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11166714"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:17:28Z","content":"It is a mother and her child funeral.  Is there really any threat.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Nicole Gagnon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61029197"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:08:01Z","content":"I am a mother and I feel her pain. Nothing should get in front of human values.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Francoise D-Couturier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38065023"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:04:54Z","content":"Its her son's funeral, how can they not let her go? \r\nI hope she can go and we can make that little difference to her. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Avi Harper","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70011425"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:27:07Z","content":"Every Canadian citizen should be given full support from our government and arrangements made for them to return to Canada unless they are charged with a serious offense, i.e. murder, drug related offenses.  The situation this young woman is in does not seem right at all.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Joan Alvarez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26932629"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:55:39Z","content":"She should be there for the funeral now.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Rob Nisbet","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71928064"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:01:50Z","content":"I have seen this kind of thing before between Canada and Cuba. It is one of the reasons I will never travel there again. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Mary Metcalfe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63919166"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:17:30Z","content":"I have also been detained in Cuba, which is a frightening experience. Mom has suffered enough, let her go home.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Alexandra  Stuart","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3270901"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:52:12Z","content":"This is a terrible story. I'm very shy to hear that there is no assistance from the Canadian Embassy in Cuba and more when I hear that the Canadian Government doesn't have a good reputation for helping Canadians in distress abroad.  This has to change !","like_count":1,"author_name":"Isabelle Racine","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69666121"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:04:57Z","content":"This is awful, I can only imagine the pain this woman is feeling... She needs to be home with her family...","like_count":1,"author_name":"kelly berger","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52552173"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:04:58Z","content":"It's just wrong what's being done to her.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Vanessa Lloyd","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78884269"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:14:43Z","content":"Every person deserves the basic right to be there when a loved one dies, Please do the right thing.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Meegan Ball","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2305949"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:45:14Z","content":"whats wrong with our canadian government ,shame on them for not helping this poor woman to get home . my heart and prayers go out to her i have burried a little son years ago . and this mother needs to be back here in canada for this so he can say goodbye to her baby boy. \r\n","like_count":1,"author_name":"gloria dian lachance","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16870092"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:37:13Z","content":"Please let the mother assist to her son's funeral this Saturday","like_count":1,"author_name":"Dianne Pitre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65592363"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:50:49Z","content":"A mom needs to put her son to rest and be there. Any country should understand that!","like_count":1,"author_name":"April Johnson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/19701536"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:01:58Z","content":"She is a mom, who has a right to say good-bye to her son. Please make this happen.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lucy Peros","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50575136"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:14:46Z","content":"It makes me sick to my stomach to even imagine not being there for my child's funeral.  Heartless and inhuman!  Certainly not proud of our Canadian Govt. in this situation.  They should be ashamed so is the Cuban Govt.\r\nMakes you think twice about visiting Cuba again!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Johanne Ramsay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/53017722"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:21:11Z","content":"One should be able to count on their govn't for help. I feel this is just a money grab from Cuban officials and has happened many times","like_count":1,"author_name":"Teresa Bloch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63612494"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:27:36Z","content":"This mother has every right to say her final goodbyes to her child, something that no parent should have to go through. Cuba has no right to detain her for this tragic accident. She should be united with her son to see him into the ever after.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Renee Linton-Parmentier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77676111"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:52:22Z","content":"As a mother my biggest worry while raising my girls was for their well being.  I truly don't know what I would have don't if I had lost a child.  I am praying that this mother will be given the chance at least be able to say her final good bye and morn her loss with people who really care and want to support her.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Violet, Patricia Cobb","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78883169"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:55:53Z","content":"Release Justine ASAP!! What is this? She did not commit a crime!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Fedor Markvardt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/53509185"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:44:44Z","content":"I am a mother. This is horrific.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Bonnie Gingras","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78882624"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:52:23Z","content":"A mother should be able to be at her sons funeral","like_count":1,"author_name":"Denise MacDonald","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77407098"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:11:24Z","content":"Canadians deserve to be helped in situations like this and that is what our Government is there for. It's lack of compassion and support generally for Canadians is disgraceful. \r\nStart the change- and make a difference!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kenneth Morris","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13057785"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:02:48Z","content":"Why do they have the right to keep her in Cuba for any reason....much less a traffic accident at which her son was killed..........where is the Canadian consulate ???????","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lynda Holst","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56318111"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:52:23Z","content":"Deepest sympathies to Justine and her family. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Don McCaw","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44817623"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:08:29Z","content":"For many reasons including because I have a son living and working in another country","like_count":1,"author_name":"Heather Grant","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69353346"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:45:26Z","content":"This is not acceptable at all.  Justin has gone through a lot of pain and should be allowed to come back to Canada","like_count":1,"author_name":"Baljit Singh","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10591355"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:51:01Z","content":"My kids & I travel abroad. It could happen to any Canadian.","like_count":1,"author_name":"shirley peters","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75764614"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:02:02Z","content":"Dont you think this mother has been through enough losing her child on vacation plus injuring herself!! The least they can do is let her go home and bury her snow at peace !!  At lease give her that for the love of God !! What a very heartbreaking and and tragic story ...","like_count":1,"author_name":"kimberley aubin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52260292"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:02:02Z","content":"I'm a daughter and a mother and I can not imagine her pain and would not wish this on anyone.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Stephanie Russell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16055026"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:40:54Z","content":"If she were American, would this be happening? At least the Americans protect their own abroad. The Canadian diplomatic core is an embarrassment in their consistency in refusing to help their own people.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Atherton Drenth","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35724624"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:08:31Z","content":"This whole situation is sad and sickens me! Free this woman let her come home to greive!!! What is wrong with this world","like_count":1,"author_name":"jennifer mcwilliams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78880489"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:02:57Z","content":"i remember exactly what i was doing on december 23rd. it was my birthday. my heart goes out to cameron, justine and their family.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Paria Karimi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66085906"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:08:15Z","content":"Human rights and...just...justice ...moral concerns!!!\r\nIncredible! ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Claudette Houde","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73164900"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:11:30Z","content":"Because I often travel and I know that our embassies have a reputation for throwing lavish parties instead of actually helping Canadians.  It also surprises me that the Cuban government would do this, as by far the greatest number of tourists are from Canada.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Andrew Critchley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47568196"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:17:45Z","content":"Come on, really......","like_count":1,"author_name":"andrew dale","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28188132"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:37:26Z","content":"We know the incredible pain from losing a child.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Linda Lowery","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52711055"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:44:49Z","content":"Allow for family to grieve","like_count":1,"author_name":"ron kanutski","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56466267"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:44:49Z","content":"Something most be done about this immediately!\r\nI want to support this petition because it's ridiculous that she is being held there without reason after loosing the most precious thing, her child, and not being able to be present at his funeral. \r\n\r\nPlease help her to return to Canada for her son's funeral! ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Anna Duran","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/53945217"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:37:28Z","content":"JUSTICE PLEASE LET HER GO...","like_count":1,"author_name":"Catherine Forand","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78882064"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:56:50Z","content":"It is important to me because I have children just like her.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Nadeeya Mosah","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72127412"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:21:33Z","content":"Friend of a Friend. Bring them home!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Bret Mercer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78881170"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:37:28Z","content":"Consular services are for all citizens. All means all. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Paul Davis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34244236"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:44:50Z","content":"A mother should be able to attend her son's funeral, without question.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Germaine Lynch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16821879"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:59:03Z","content":"It seems like not allowing Justine the opportunity to attend the burial of her son makes an already tragic situation even more devastating. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Brynne Scott-Zwicker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59714523"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:56:53Z","content":"Because this is his son and he should be there for his funeral!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"christy michalenko","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58310721"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:27:56Z","content":"every mother should have the right to say goodbye to the child when something like this happens! Justine Davis should not be held and forced to miss her sons funeral. she did not kill her child. its was a motor accident. this is horrible. She needs to be released and sent home so she can be with her family during this time! This is very unfair!! my thoughts and prayers go out to Justine Davis and her family!!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Amanda Hiuser","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78881473"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:08:21Z","content":"It is the least this mother could ask for...to bid farewell to her sweet deceased baby boy!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Janet Murungi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75082123"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:11:35Z","content":"I am a mother and would want to be able to attend my child's funeral.  This woman's needs closure somehow.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Joelle Plamondon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77238668"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:44:53Z","content":"She is injured send her home to attend her son's funeral as well","like_count":1,"author_name":"susan turnbull","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12754022"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:45:52Z","content":"As a mother, my heart goes to Justine. May God give her strength and all the love to get through!    As a Canadian citizen, I am outraged of the way of how the authorities are dealing (better said, NOT dealing with safety and care of Canadians. Shame on them!  I'm never going to vacation in Cuba again, and I'm going to make sure to convince everybody I know not to. This is my boycott to Cuban authorities as they live mostly out of tourism, and I wish all Canadians would follow ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Corina Man","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78879329"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:08:47Z","content":"Not only thus story heart breaking for the family it is upsetting the Canadian government is not helping this family in a time of need.  ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Rahel Eshete","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3299595"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:17:54Z","content":"I would want to be able to attend my own childs funeral if that happened to me. No parent no matter what happens in life should still be able to lay their child to rest.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Sara Mercer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78885406"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:33:24Z","content":"CANADA IS OBLIGATED TO ASSIST JUSTINE IN MATTERS, WHETHER HEALTH, FINANCIAL, LEGAL AND LAWFUL.... THIS IS A CONSTITUTIONAL OBLIGATION FROM QUEEN ELIZABETH SWORN STATEMENT WHEN SHE TOOK HER OATH......","like_count":1,"author_name":"Wilfred Leger","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57139127"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:49:03Z","content":"Although Cuba has its rules and regulations, please appeal to the Cuban government for humanitarian reasons","like_count":1,"author_name":"Susan Surtel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15128723"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:15:00Z","content":"This accident was not Justine's fault.","like_count":1,"author_name":"marian nyitrai","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7315678"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:17:56Z","content":"As a mother I am mortified in 2014 this crap is still going on.  How very tragic!!!!  I am also a travel agent and have to re-think booking people to Cuba.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jeanne Haagen-Lebert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8243538"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:03:19Z","content":"Ok what ever the hold up is....do you not think this poor woman has paid the ultimate price...the death of a child. Wake up world, let her do what needs to be done, why is it when it comes to common sense the world has no compassion...unless it comes to making money. Be wise let her be free. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Rob Freeman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27071508"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:08:52Z","content":"The suffering of losing her child is hard enough but being prevented from his funeral is cruel.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lisa Cascanette","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78880509"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:56:14Z","content":"I'm a mother!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Scott Carl","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78236763"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:21:46Z","content":"It's a human situation and so whatever can humanely be done to bring solace to an injured, grieving mother, and her family, it should be done. Isn't this why people pay taxes? Not to send Politicians to the bank.   ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Stacy James Fry","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66030796"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:57:12Z","con