a Canadian want to visit other countries, as we hope their people visit us, then I would like to believe and know that my home government would be there to support me.  I sign my name in the hopes that this woman can be home for the funeral. Why is she being detained? Why not let her come home? What does Cuba hope to gain by keeping her there? Maybe they would like less and less Canadians visiting their country - who wants to when this is how we are treated? You want us to come and visit and spend our money there, Cuba, get with the program and make it amenable for us to want to visit. I, for one, go to countries that treat me better than a criminal!!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Diane Nickolizen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78880549"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:33:44Z","content":"I am a human being and a father.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Phuntsok Choephel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47907799"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:09:36Z","content":"It is not right to keep someone detained indefinitely","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lisa Fowler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51070754"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:18:10Z","content":"Justice and compassion.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Nelson Rodriguez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15857462"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:16:15Z","content":"Concern for the state of health of those still alive should take precedent.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Alan Merrilees","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61750238"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:29:12Z","content":"Tragic incident. Family Values.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Scott Graham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/64332539"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:41:55Z","content":"This family needs to be together, and Justine Davis needs to come home to Canada - because that's what she wants!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Tracy Amirault","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73652953"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T22:56:34Z","conten