se the chapters to devastating circumstances in order to move on.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vanessa K Baird","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52981792"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T17:00:39Z","content":"Because no one deserves to be going through this. Especially a mother who has just lost her son. Please help her!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nadiya Virani","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22258023"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T17:38:06Z","content":"Justine has been a friend for well over 10 years and she is an AMAZING mother and friend. This entire predicament with her not being able to come back to Canada for her son's funeral is ABSURD! This all was a TERRIBLE, HORRIBLE ACCIDENT and everyone knows this. To keep her from burying her son and having this day of closure at the very LEAST is just in every possible way DISGUSTING! So PLEASE I am BEGGING who ever you are that has the authority to release her to PLEASE do so, even if it be only for her son's funeral!!! Sincerely Caprice Letourneau","like_count":0,"author_name":"Caprice Letourneau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78738347"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:40:20Z","content":"Legalistic or not. Compassionate grounds are indicated here. Shall we get the media involved on this every day and may affect tourism to Cuba","like_count":0,"author_name":"Donna Young","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68605495"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:40:43Z","content":"How can you do this to a mother?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laura Robinson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7281023"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:35:52Z","content":"The saddest circumstances I have heard for a while, God Bless Justine and her family at this time. I pray that she is able to recover from this grief in its time.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Winona Farah","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78249162"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T22:47:59Z","content":"A mother should be at home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bobbi Mills","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/46563073"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:42:05Z","content":"it is wrong what is being done to that poor woman","like_count":0,"author_name":"kim thorne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48436982"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:38:27Z","content":"I have a son too.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Caity Powell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78899852"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:33:20Z","content":"<a href=\"mailto:rdechamplain@hotmail.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">rdechamplain@hotmail.com</a>","like_count":0,"author_name":"R de Champlain","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51740182"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:50:02Z","content":"Should not have happened.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lorna Barrington","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78911136"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:04:58Z","content":"Please free Justine to be able to be in Canada for her son's funeral. It is bad enough that she lost her son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Einas Keswani","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/40825429"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:53:46Z","content":"Because if we cannot expect help from the Canadian Embassies, it makes it very unsafe to travel above the fact that these parents are being treated like criminals in their time of mourning!  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deborah Lea-Boisvert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10497804"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T04:00:14Z","content":"this is insane.....and the fact that no officials are helping  or even responding is beyond me. Where are her human rights.....her canadian rights....any person has the right to bury their child. even if they are incarcerated.... im mad just reading this....","like_count":0,"author_name":"lara-lynn liddiard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21082449"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:10:38Z","content":"As a parent my heart breaks for this poor mom who is being treated so unfairly. Allow her to come and say goodbye to her beautiful son. ","