ppen to anyone. Don't vacation in Cuba. Boycott the country.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jo-Anne  Absolon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7509324"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:10:21Z","content":"Because I am a mother with a young child.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pia Natividad","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37185605"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:28:36Z","content":"Death is permanent and so is the heartache of losing a child, this mother deserves better from our country!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amanda Charron","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/54808788"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:08:58Z","content":"Mourning is a long and difficult process especially when you losse a child. Funeral is a step that can be crucial and it seem normal for a mother to have this right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Martin Camirand","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/40699712"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:14:14Z","content":"Ms. Davis needs closure!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kellie Williams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78897107"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:37:30Z","content":"Entre canadien, ca serait bien de s'aider et ca inclut notre gouvernement.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gilbert Arsenault","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/49482522"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:06:41Z","content":"a mother has the right to be their for her child no matter what and no one should step in the way of that.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sophia Martin-Morice","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12877679"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:08:46Z","content":"This mother should be allowed closure.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carrilyn Fisk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69361629"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:08:06Z","content":"In the last 5-6 years our Canadian Embassey staff throughout the world appear to be avoiding help Canadian citizens in need to an extent that leaves not only troubled but ashamed. This mother needs help and certainly does not appear \"to have violated\" any laws so why the lack of support?? Please help her.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathryn Hall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10780304"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T15:45:26Z","content":"I am a mom to a toddler right now and I couldn't imagine not being able to give my daughter the respect for all she has given to me, with a proper goodbye..I would rather die myself and them meet with her...If we are human, why is this sooo inhumane???","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah nunes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78721191"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:37:10Z","content":"It is bad enough that she lost her handsome little boy, but now Cuba won't let her come home to bury her baby. This is an outrage. Well if Cuba is worried about there tourism states well they are just making it worse by not letting her come home to bury her son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Angela Frangipane`","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78857214"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:11:01Z","content":"This child deserves to be buried by his mother! Shame on the officials that are preventing this!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"jennifer cassar","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78863994"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:33:24Z","content":"<a href=\"mailto:mevebd@hotmail.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">mevebd@hotmail.com</a>","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marie-\u00c8ve Bertrand","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35282109"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:57:36Z","content":"I can't believe that the Cuban Government doesn't do more for Canadians. I will never visit Cuba. I thought it was a much friendlier place.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andrew Grant","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26930727"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:44:55Z","content":"A mother should be able to be at the funeral of her son","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deacon Henry C. Verschuren","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31600507"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:34:15Z","content":"Dont GO to Cuba","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rob Telford","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35990733"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:47:10Z","content":"My heart goes out to Justine.  This is a question of humanity and humanity must always trump legalities.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kevin Galalae","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65939100"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:55:51Z","content":"it was an unfortunate accident, my heart breaks for her because she must be suffering so much already. no mother should lose a child , its her son...let her go home!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Luisa Gonzalez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78894914"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:28:58Z","content":"The lack of empathy by the Cubans, and the total disregard by the Canadian government for one of their own, is inexcusable.  This is clearly a tragedy, and shame on those who have created more grief and despair of a hearthbroken Mother.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Johnson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78898764"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:08:46Z","content":"If she is being held there for no apparent reason,someone in Cuba should be held responsible for that alone..Heartbreaking this young woman would not be allowed home for her child's funeral,she should be allowed home this is WRONG!!!!!   I will make sure tp put this on my list of places never to VACATION and hopefully a lot of others will to...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brenda Stretch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76909467"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:02:15Z","content":"This is heartbreaking and wrong, The Canadian Government should be involved!\r\n\r\nBarb Robins","like_count":0,"author_name":"barb robins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60118786"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T12:48:03Z","content":"This is a mom who was just on vacation and had an accident.  This mom needs to be home for her childs funeral.  I can not imagine what she is going through and how she is being treated.  Please please please help her.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Clemmer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78703272"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:20:12Z","content":"Oh my goodness, Justine, my heart aches for you - I'm so sorry for the loss of your little boy and this unimaginable situation you & your family are in. I'm sending all my love & prayers to you and wish there was more I could do. I'll share your story as much as I can today! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Justine  McKnight","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26806025"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:57:02Z","content":"This is a parents worst nightmare.  Something must be done!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nikki Nicholls","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70792424"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:34:51Z","content":"This woman and this boy deserve his body to come home. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tiffany weller","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78746805"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:51:18Z","content":"its heartbreaking ","like_count":0,"author_name":"cindy f","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38496628"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:05:13Z","content":"Get this mom home!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marisa Bernardo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78759432"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:10:25Z","content":"Outrageous.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gordon Ross","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72425837"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:04:26Z","content":"Because Justine has been through enough and should be able to at least come home to lay her some to rest. This is such a tragic story,my heart breaks for all those who know her personally I couldn't even imagine being in her shoes. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amy Verge","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78786492"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:41:33Z","content":"I don't know this woman , but I am also a mother an keeping mother from there childs funeral is just wrong and heartless in s