rt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78710779"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T16:17:22Z","content":"Because its important to my cousin who was a friend of hers and its a terribly sad situation that no one should have to go through","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lindsay Montforts","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78726082"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:04:29Z","content":"Bring back our grieving Canadians !","like_count":0,"author_name":"Darren Giddings","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43185290"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:18:59Z","content":"Being a mother you must send this women home so she can say goodbye to her son, this treatment that she is enduring is not humane. She belongs at home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joe Anne Souray","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71203699"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:38:14Z","content":"I am a mother too","like_count":0,"author_name":"Annabelle Thiebaux","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34713126"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T01:11:11Z","content":"Let her come home. how can you just sit back and do this to someone that went through so much. My God have a heart ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Antonio Parente","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78791842"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:34:16Z","content":"Empathy. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Meg Conway","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29943619"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:01:21Z","content":"My child died in an accident and I can't imagine what she is going through. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brenda Hughes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37996517"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:03:52Z","content":"It is important to me because the loss of a child is the greatest loss any parent will ever suffer. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bryan Benson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77389140"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:54:55Z","content":"She just lost her son. She need family and friends. They also have no right not hold her. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tammy Chaney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78902487"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:04:09Z","content":"No mother should ever be held from attending a funeral of her own child!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tynan Thacker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78903839"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:17:23Z","content":"recently travelled in Cuba and can not begin to imagine what the family is going through.   She is a friend of a friend.","like_count":0,"author_name":"evan dwinnell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17202478"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:16:20Z","content":"I have children and i something like this happened to me I would want the same help in return! It was an accident and not intentional. Let her be there at least for her funeral and if anything else bring her back after to conclude the investigation.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Toneya Nunez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78916087"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:30:36Z","content":"I'm Canadian and so is she, we look after our own especially under these circumstances.","like_count":0,"author_name":"larry lefave","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69430661"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:30:28Z","content":"because the CAN Gov needs to step up for one of their tax paying citizens","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tom Gyorko","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69183860"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:34:53Z","content":"I couldn't imagine being in this mother's position, having to bury her beautiful son. Let alone being unable to attend his funeral. The cuban and Canadian governments need to work together to do what they can to help this mother be with her son when he is laid to rest. Please consider and do what needs to be done to expedite this process. Her travels are not a harm to the investigation and eventually she will be permitted home, so this needs to happen quickly for her own personal benefit. Every official should put themselves in her situation and ask themselves if THEY would let the paperwork and red tape stop them from burying their child.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christella Morris","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51132327"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:25:30Z","content":"I hope that will force the Canadian embassy staff to help Justine so she can come home for Cameron's funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"PETER STEWART","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47022385"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:44:50Z","content":"As a mother I can't imagine having to endure such a tragic, heartbreaking loss and yourself having to heal from such serious injuries as well...and then to have to face political crap on top of it all is unforgiveable.  Please help this mother grieve properly and be there with her son and family.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bev Waters","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5281114"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:08:50Z","content":"Who wouldn't know why. It's evident !\r\nCuba should fear retaliation from tourists if Canadian request is not heeded","like_count":0,"author_name":"Paul De Larminat","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69937718"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:38:19Z","content":"There is no reason for this woman to not be allowed to come home and she should be there to say goodbye to her son. My heart goes out to this family in the time of mourning. We should be doing everything we can to help and not make this worse.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tamara Turcotte","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22736789"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:07:52Z","content":"because a mother should be allowed to be at her son's funeral...Cuban officials have no heart apparently!","like_count":0,"author_name":"rose madurski","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78893889"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:26:09Z","content":"thats not right","like_count":0,"author_name":"dave brown","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78872861"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:50:06Z","content":"she needs to be home for her sons funeral ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Louise Savoie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78765695"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:22:54Z","content":"<a href=\"mailto:sergiopoulin@hotmail.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">sergiopoulin@hotmail.com</a>","like_count":0,"author_name":"Serge Poulin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63870503"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:42:07Z","content":"Cause it is very important to this mom to get to her sons' funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karen Gilbank","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48695485"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:51:05Z","content":"Again, Foreign Affairs Canada are dragging their heels.   It's embarrassing.  As a proud Canadian this is unacceptable.  A little boy has died in Cuba and his mom wants to be at his \r\nfuneral.  Lesson to learn - don't travel to Cuba - their laws are Napoleonic - a person is guilty until they prove their innocence.  It's the opposite of our laws.  Bring Justine home to Toronto for Saturday. Feb. 8th. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne Brigham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29899535"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:25:44Z","content":"Canadians going to Cuba on vacation is a large part of Cuba's economy--and this is how they treat these tourists!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maria Medley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31573511"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T02:37:41Z","content":"she is a friend of a friend and this is an injustice. plus she is a grief-stricken mother who just lost her young son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karen McCrindle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78799403"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:06:43Z","content":"She is a mother. She is grieving and must be with her family. This will haunt her for the rest of her life if she is not present to bury her child.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amy Bolden","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5581874"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:10:52Z","content":"Parents should not outlive 