uld let her go right NOW","like_count":0,"author_name":"Monique Beriau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78913366"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:22:18Z","content":"Why should this Canadian be detained for no reason??","like_count":0,"author_name":"Denise Barker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78917267"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T13:28:24Z","content":"Cause I have a child and if some thing wrong where in she pass I would like to see her for the last time too so I believe she deserve the same ","like_count":0,"author_name":"shellion scott","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78849132"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:53:20Z","content":"no mother should not be able to be at their childs funeral. a mother should not have to lay a child to rest, but in the case that they have to no matter who you are you should  be able go. this is juts crazy. what is the Canadian embassy there for..... i thought they are there to help us Canadians in need. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"ashley stevenson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78858455"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:57:45Z","content":"This woman needs to be home, please help her.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Tamburro","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60665652"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:11:40Z","content":"To allow for this mental suffering of a mother that is already enduring the tragic death of her son, is savage and inhumane. To forbid her passage home is even more so disturbing. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Veronica Apple","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78743371"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:33:30Z","content":"Sadly these two people are separated by death but why should they be separated for the funeral???\r\nWhy do we pay for an Embassy in Cuba or anywhere else if our government is proving time and time again to be totally useless in helping Canadians abroad?\r\nSadly our government departments are only interested in themselves at the expense of Canadians.","like_count":0,"author