03:20:18Z","content":"Because I feel that she should be there for her son's fun","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patricia Martinez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78916852"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:53:09Z","content":"I can't think of a reason for it not to be important\u2026. If you guys don't do something about this your wrong..","like_count":0,"author_name":"Angelo Marchelletta","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78923106"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:57:10Z","content":"She is going to so much as it is, she has the right to move back to Canada.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cleusa Oliveira","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29272014"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:32:06Z","content":"I'm a mother, I couldn't imagine loosing a child, what's more unimaginable is not being able to say goodbye. Every parent has a right to closer.","like_count":0,"author_name":"jessica yerxa","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62174829"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:37:38Z","content":"No Mother should have to bury her child,let alone be kept in another Country and not allowed to go too his funeral!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandra Murphy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78867954"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:21:46Z","content":"Justine Davis should be able to leave Cuba she did nothing wrong and needs to be home where she belongs especially to attend her sons funeral on Sat Feb 82014","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne-Marie MacGillivary","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78869867"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:38:23Z","content":"I am also a mother.  It would be devastating to me that a simple accident in a foreign country could allow them to not send me home for my son's funeral.  The Canadian Embassy needs to provide Canadians traveling abroad the support they need, particularly at times like this.  We offer support to refugees, but cannot help our own??","like_count":0,"author_name":"Wendy Richardson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73072413