o has visited Cuba ,would hope that their government show the same compassion.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Angelo Pontello","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45575637"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:34:34Z","content":"Justine's rights need to be respected. If she is not being held or charged she should be released to leave immediately. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer  Rankin ","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16761772"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T17:56:38Z","content":"I'm a mother to a beautiful little boy, and God forbid, he ever passed away before me, I would be heart broken if I didn't get the closure I needed.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Danielle Howlett-Nezezon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26837216"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:41:23Z","content":"Our government should have more influence in helping our citizens, especially when so many vacation in Cuba, thus helping the economy. Cuban officials should be more forthcoming.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joanne Marson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70138465"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:42:46Z","content":"She has the right to be at her son's funeral , this whole thing sounds like a lot of crap. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jim Kirk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23238765"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:32:18Z","content":"So sad!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susie Booth","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75557499"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:22:54Z","content":"it could be me and family or any other Canadians","like_count":0,"author_name":"francis joseph","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6974640"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:59:30Z","content":"I am a mother and cannot imagine not being able to attend my own child'd funeral. And from what I read, there seems to be no reason to keep the mother in Cuba.  Please Canadians, help Justine.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Francyne Charbonneau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44895833"},{"created_at":"20