/reasons?page=5&page_size=500","total_pages":9,"reasons":[{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:44:47Z","content":"I sign this petition and sympathy for Justine but the Cuban diplomatic/judicial system is incredibly barbaric and backwards, and the Canadian Embassy seems to be there more as a symbol than as a functioning arm of our govt. Good luck.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Walter Hildreth","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52884206"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:51:39Z","content":"No mother should have to miss her child's funeral, this woman has been through enough!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kara Wieler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11313862"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:10:43Z","content":"It is a human issue. Please let her go.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Eva Radford","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37778707"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:48:24Z","content":"she needs to be home","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carol Peters","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43264847"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:19:59Z","content":"No mother should be kept from her child's final moments.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amy Brown","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71581566"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:37:22Z","content":"This is common sense.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kimmo Dancey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78878916"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:02:36Z","content":"I would hope should I be in a similar situation with my child, my government would support me.  I travel a lot with my child and would be absolutely devastated to miss the funeral and have no interference from my embassy officials.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Sawyer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62864820"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T04:14:11Z","content":"To be human.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Daniel Omiyi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78807181"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:38:37Z","content":"It was an ACCIDENT!  She lost her son.  If they do not have any evidence of drugs or alcohol in her blood then RELEASE HER!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Betty Costilla","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78899885"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:22:45Z","content":"I have a 3yr old daughter, I can relate as a mother. She has every right to pay her respects to her son, she has done nothing wrong. Im praying!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sheena Cappello","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78906636"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:33:33Z","content":"Would you be at your childs funeral? ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jesse Alfaro","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78908503"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:39:14Z","content":"Please let Justine come home and say her final goodbyes to her beloved son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Edison","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78909237"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:05:16Z","content":"The Canadian government needs to take immediate action to bring Justine home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathleen Hay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70142086"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:41:45Z","content":"the Government needs to protect Canadians where ever they are !","like_count":0,"author_name":"alexis sexton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78920989"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T15:52:49Z","content":"Canadian citizen having no rights in cuba!","like_count":0,"author_name":"matt jolie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76929184"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:49:07Z","content":"What a tragedy, but it's even sadder that our Government strands people like Justine abroad during her time of need, without help. I support this petition and hope she can come home in time.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alena Wickware","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11019066"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:58:03Z","content":"I am a Mother and Grandmother. I feel for Justine.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Camille Hines","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61710941"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:46:49Z","content":"No mother should have to bury there child let alone not be there for their Funeral. This is deplorable!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jenny O'Gorman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78873864"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:33:00Z","content":"as a mother i can not even imagine what she is going thru. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stephnaie Carberry","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78763416"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:23:25Z","content":"She is a victim herself and in a lot of pain. Her detainment is illogical. Bring her back home to Canada ASAP.","like_count":0,"author_name":"adnan shah","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65475551"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T21:07:59Z","content":"What is happening to this mother is outrageous and unacceptable and she should be supported by her country no matter her skin tone ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Natalie Bray","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78766387"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:19:33Z","content":"Hope she can get home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"David Grinton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13395220"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:19:30Z","content":"She should be with her family and friends at this difficult time.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julie Fitzsimmons","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78787840"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T01:51:54Z","content":"As a mother, my heart aches for Justine Davis.  She has lost her beautiful son and is now unable to kiss his sweet head before he is laid to rest.  Please Madame Gagnon, have mercy on this mother and support her in returning home to Canada.  \r\nSincerely, \r\nJodie Golini \r\nMother to Francis (2) and Julian (6 months)","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jodie Golini","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78795605"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:29:58Z","content":"Human compassion","like_count":0,"author_name":"Grace Tallar","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47494600"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:02:39Z","content":"has she not suffered enough already!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dote Werner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6319324"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:07:44Z","content":"This just adds more sorrow to an unimaginable tragedy for any parent. Please allow this grieving mother to go home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pam Woodall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2087945"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T05:32:50Z","content":"if there was no ill-intent, then why is she being held, the mother will have to live with this loss for the rest of her life, she has to be able to morn with family and friends, and our so call Canadian reps should get the fuck off their ass and do their job for a change\r\n ","like_count":0,"author_name":"dean desbois","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78812309"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:27:18Z","content":"This is unacceptable CUBA, THIS IS HER SON. She needs to go home and be with her family. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cristina Estrada","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73253991"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:35:34Z","content":"This is a family tragedy not a criminal issue.  This is not justice","like_count":0,"author_name":"Fred Worm","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73864953"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:53:57Z","content":"No child should be without her Mother, when she only has so long to live!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Penny Malott","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75618174"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T16:22:22Z","content":"I am a mother myself, no mother should ever have to bury their child. Or miss the chance to do so and have one last goodbye ","like_count":0,"author_name":"nicole geary","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78726808"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:07:55Z","content":"This is disgusting to treat a young mother like this during such a tragic and heart-rending time. Please let her fly back for her son's funeral. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Natalie Stocker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48280976"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:11:58Z","content":"This woman has just lost two important people to her in the span of two months.  She is grieving.  She is willing to follow the legal process, but wanted to be here for her son's funeral.  Morally and ethically it is wrong to prevent her from attending.  If something binding could be arranged that would allow her return to Cuba afterward, from which she could not get out of, I do not see why she should need to remain there until the legal process unfolds.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathy Arnusch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44878723"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:38:04Z","content":"The government needs to act more quickly and forcefully to help Canadians abroad in such situations where they are innocent.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Serpone","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43196112"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:13:40Z","content":"It is time the Canadian government gets off their ass and demands Justine to come home...if it were a family member of a politician you can bet your bottom dollar that they would be home already. To Harper - get off your lazy ass and demand results now!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Richard May","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77697630"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:29:59Z","content":"Humanitarian reasons","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ariel Kahana","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/67253090"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:25:04Z","content":"im a mother of 3 god forbid something tragic like this happen and mom must be suffering in every way hope she makes it to see her son for the last time","like_count":0,"author_name":"yesenia infante","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78907069"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:31:28Z","content":"I'm a mother and have empathy of how devastated she is right now.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Olga Santiago","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78908138"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:43:39Z","content":"I have visited Cuba on two occasions. I found it to be a beautiful Country with beautiful people! I remember being told by a Tour Bus Operator that Cuba depends on Canadian tourist dollars to survive. I am asking Yves Gagnon to remind Cuba of the historically close ties between our Countries and their need for our continued tourist support and to DEMAND that they SEND JUSTINE DAVIS HOME TO BURY HER BABY!! If Cuba does not comply with her request, then there should be an Official Canadian Boycott of tourism to Cuba! I, for one, will not go back to Cuba if they fail in this humane obligation to send Justine come home NOW! So very sorry for your loss, Justine and family.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nora Walsh","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/60801674"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:07:58Z","content":"As a  mother, I cannot bear to think of the grief this mother must be experiencing.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Helen Bacik","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/67228234"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:21:51Z","content":"She deserves this!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amanda Doiron","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74531868"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:36:54Z","content":"This mother needs to be able to properly grieve the loss of her son after such an unfortunate tragedy.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Peddle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78865238"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:58:08Z","content":"I would be devistated if I was the mother and had to miss my child's funeral","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cheryl Durant","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31634953"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:41:10Z","content":"I'M A HUMAN BEING...","like_count":0,"author_name":"JACQUES KIROUAC","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72170727"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:07:03Z","content":"No mother should be denied the right to say goodbye to their child! God bless her and her family &lt;3","like_count":0,"author_name":"Viviana Hernandez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73055459"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:32:01Z","content":"Because family comes first and the mother is fighting to be with her dead son that's bad enough for a mother I pray for her to be strong a mother should never have to bury her own child","like_count":0,"author_name":"fernando chavarria","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37164161"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:15:04Z","content":"My family visits Cuba & have heard about this type of thing --","like_count":0,"author_name":"Russ Salo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/64603464"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:45:46Z","content":"If a crime has been committed, it against Justine and her son. Spare this family additional pain and release her immediately. There is no end to the pain she will endure the rest of her life for her loss. How dare you add to this woman's suffering.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jane Tanner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78893909"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:33:30Z","content":"As a mother myself, I can only imagine the hell she is going through. Let her go home and be with family.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lisa Kent","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78899246"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:00:50Z","content":"I'm a parent","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lance Wilson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78903365"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:07:41Z","content":"This is important to me because no one should be prevented to bury one's child. The mother should be allowed to be at the child's funeral. I truly hope that Canadian officials will put all their  weight on Cuban officials for this mother to be at the child's funeral. And I hope the Cuban officials will be human enough to hear and understand this mother's distress.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jean Razafindambo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45555839"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:14:03Z","content":"Because Canadian embassy sould be ashamed of what they are doing! Wake up!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rapha\u00ebl Thouin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14384005"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:27:19Z","content":"Being a mother myself, there is no horror, nothing you could do to this woman worse than what she is going through. Let her have some closure before deciding what happens to her in Cuba. If she turns out to be innocent, it would be a grave injustice to have allowed her to miss her son's funeral. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kristen Lea","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12633683"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:35:49Z","content":"She is a grieving mother that should be released to be able to find some closure for her and her son. It is bad enough that an accident took his life, why is she being detained, possible politics ??","like_count":0,"author_name":"nick andrews","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78908860"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:31:37Z","content":"I am outraged that our Canadian government does not do more to help Canadians abroad in distress","like_count":0,"author_name":"Charlene Johnson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/64968362"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:43:54Z","content":"closure. I lost my son and it was not an option to be able to say good-bye to  MY BABY","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rebecca Miller","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78921392"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:42:32Z","content":"Just simply it is the right thing to do. To let this mother say good bye to her son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"sue hosson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/40635366"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:26:37Z","content":"I am just wondering why \"free Justine Davis\" meant? She was a victim she is free to leave Cuba as she was just a visitor.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Meliza Mateo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74816865"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T17:41:12Z","content":"A mother should be allowed to be there at the funeral of her son, for the Canadian government not to help is horrible. Get this women home so she can say good bye to her baby","like_count":0,"author_name":"Annie Dawkins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59908962"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:16:51Z","content":"I'm sure she feels guilt already just for having the accident.  i feel she should be able to bury her son and put closer and then deal with whatever needs to be dealt with.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Monette  Gould","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28277905"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:00:53Z","content":"It is heartbreaking that Justine could miss her son's funeral and be denied the opportunity to grieve his tragic death surrounded by the love and support of friends and family.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marilyn Towndrow","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52820198"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:22:30Z","content":"Every mother as sad as it is, should be allowed to go to her own  childs funeral. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"nicola wrana","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72220794"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:06:00Z","content":"it is wrong  to bury your child without attending....no parent should ever have to bury their child","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tina Yetman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61995462"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T03:59:22Z","content":"she should be able to get home....","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christine Hailstone","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61992059"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T04:45:10Z","content":"This mother belongs home with Her Son...to say goodbye at the very least!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rosanne Farano-Romanino","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78809406"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:51:58Z","content":"Because it's not right.  She needs help getting home to people who can help her thru this.  Even from perfect strangers.  I want that for her.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kim Chase","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78901972"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:29:20Z","content":"This is, as Quincy says, shameful!  What is wrong with our government?  They are suppose to protect and support their citizens when they are vulnerable and in need of help.  Those in charge:  get off your laurels and do what needs to be done to bring this poor woman home so she can lay her son to rest.  Hasn't she endured enough suffering?  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laura Thomas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76631296"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T14:25:46Z","content":"because she is a mom that lost her son and needs to be at his funeral not detained in Cuba.This is just not right. She has been through enough already.Please help her get out..","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mary-Anne  Froebe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12432325"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T15:15:59Z","content":"This is an injustice for this young mother to be detained in Cuba","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deborah Longshaw","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78717666"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T16:26:00Z","content":"Because it's the right thing to do. Send her home Cuba. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joel Knapp","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78727309"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:27:58Z","content":"humanity!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kelly Dodds","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61235792"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T17:38:25Z","content":"This story brings tears to my eyes as a mother, as a woman, as a human. This is heartbreaking. We have to help this woman. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Imahn Khan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35510365"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T19:24:49Z","content":"This situation is horrific. I cannot even imagine this family's pain. It is absolutely ridiculous that both governments can't find a way to resolve this issue and get this poor woman home. I have been to Cuba  several times and love the country and its people....but this disgusts me! As a mom of three this story broke my heart. Officials on both sides need to ask themselves what they would do if it was their own child. Where is the compassion? GET SOMETHING DONE!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nancy Pase","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32173110"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:10:49Z","content":"A mother lost her child, she should be present for the funeral AT HOME","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michael Boctor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/48513826"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:10:06Z","content":"Because this child's Mom must have the right to say goodbye physically and emotionally.  Ms. Davis has suffered so much already.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Janet Inglis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78760248"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T19:35:28Z","content":"The Canadian Government should be helping this young mother to come home and heal, and say goodbye to her son.  So very sad :(","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathryn Kellner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59973214"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:17:27Z","content":"A mother has to be there for her most difficult thing she will ever have to face.  She will not forgive herself if she's not there.  I'm sure she'll blame herself for the accident but she needs some closure.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dana Deschamps","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11491229"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:23:29Z","content":"Let this young Mother be release so Justine and Her Son can be reunited !! This is so important, that Justine spends those last hours by Her Son's Side!! PLEASE MAKE THIS HAPPEN!!!!! R.I.P. Cameron &lt;3","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda cormack","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26486856"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:42:37Z","content":"I am a MOM....","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sue Lee","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78876408"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T20:54:44Z","content":"Justine Davis should be able to go to the burial of her son plain and simple. Canadian politicians should be ashamed of their track record with helping Canadians in need abroad!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Allan MacDonald","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73557156"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:31:38Z","content":"No Mother should be denied the right to attend their child's funeral. If in fact it was an accident and they had no malicious intent that Mother needs to be at the funeral to put her son to rest. I hope that this family can find peace and that justice will happen.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Siobhan Otter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/67151469"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:40:36Z","content":"It is a small way that I can offer my assistance and support to this family in their time of need.   I would hope that everyone would feel compelled to act if given the chance to assist.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jim Antle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56808894"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:38:54Z","content":"Every mother should be allowed to be at her own son's funeral.  Get her home so they can be together.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andrea Nadeau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78893260"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:59:55Z","content":"Justine seems to be being held unjustly and needs to home for the funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Christensen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78396191"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:05:08Z","content":"It's devastating to lose a child.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bill Bell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7717230"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:18:14Z","content":"This mother should be able to leave Cuba and return to Canada in time to bury her son. It is all so tragic and made worse by the fact that she is being detained there.","like_count":0,"author_name":"BECKY PAUL","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30585635"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T04:28:41Z","content":"It's important because as Canadians we need to support each other and get the government support we deserve and expect from our government. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Daniela Pantaleo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34842825"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:49:47Z","content":"this poor woman needs to be with family at a time like this-just devastating and she had her boy's helmet on so she was taking care of him-LET HER COME HOME!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patricia Chapman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78901633"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T06:28:54Z","content":"To loose a child, especially one so young, is devastating. To not be able to attend his funeral so much more heart break than anyone should endure. The Cuban government needs to do what's right, and release Justine Davis on compassionate grounds.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joan L. MacDonald","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68749518"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:18:23Z","content":"Another example of our government's failure.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Margaret Paul","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57950759"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:33:37Z","content":"Because no-one should be should be restrained from attending their child's funeral, it the final goodbye & give closer.  We had a member of our extended family die in Cuba & it too weeks to get his body home to his family, putting everyone under a great strain.   Why have a Canadian Embassy there if they can't help. Please help Justine say goodbye to her son. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vi Roberts","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78908512"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T13:45:59Z","content":"This is a mother whose child has died.  It is a necessity for her to be there.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lisa Hildred","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78708442"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:00:00Z","content":"This is a slam dunk. Help her come home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Peter Kenter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/49955926"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T17:48:17Z","content":"A pa