ithout his mother by his side.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lori Nicholls-Kerec","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78852660"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:55:45Z","content":"the pain of losing a child is incomprehensible to me and being held in a foreign country while my son was to be buried is a wound far far worse than any broken bone!  Compassion must be granted.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patricia Meindl","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47657060"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:33:33Z","content":"Doesn't she have enough pain to cope with already?  Let her get home to grieve.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gerda  Toffoli","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7785271"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:22:02Z","content":"As a fellow Canadian living abroad I hope the Canadian government can look after its citizens while still respecting the laws of other countries.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Russel Fleming","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50138562"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:40:03Z","content":"Mom and her need to say good-bye to her child.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jane Rennie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32081376"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:07:14Z","content":"I think it's very important that a mother be able to bury her son.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Crystal Rucha","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29980182"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:31:48Z","content":"A mother should at least be able to bury her child.  This is unbelieveable","like_count":0,"author_name":"Barbara Swyer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74243702"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:37:33Z","content":"This is so sad, it would be way worse for the mother to not be able to attend her sons funeral.  I hope the petition works.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kate Livesey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/59089780"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:12:11Z","content":"A MOTHER SHOULD BE ABLE TO ATTEND HER SON'S FUNERAL!!!!  SHAME ON CUBA AND SHAME 