er son.  That is inhumane.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Crystal M","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78779077"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:01:55Z","content":"becvause i think she should be able if she is well to go to her son funeral","like_count":0,"author_name":"samantha smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78786257"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:13:25Z","content":"This mom needs to be with her child, Please gave her that comfort to bury the child","like_count":0,"author_name":"ann Bis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78787307"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T02:13:25Z","content":"it should be so important to everyone. this is so wrong, and unacceptable!","like_count":0,"author_name":"lynne long","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78797363"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:42:28Z","content":"To have a mother trapped in another country and unable to attend her son's funeral is unbelievable. Unless there is evidence that she intentionally caused an accident, what possible reason is there to keep her in Cuba?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nathaniel O'Neill","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66716279"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:48:47Z","content":"This mother should be allowed to attend her son's funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jacqueline Geoffroy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/42541238"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:45:53Z","content":"freedom and justice","like_count":0,"author_name":"nancy cleaves","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/72324577"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T14:37:52Z","content":"She deserves to come home!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chris Loach","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34844098"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:24:33Z","content":"This tragedy is needlessly compounded by the inhumane treatment of a grieving mother who has the right to lay her son to rest.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne Porretta","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17206519"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T16:37:26Z","content":"Pau