her who has suffered enough. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lina Walters","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62862574"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:42:28Z","content":"This is unacceptable. Any mother must be given the privilege of going to their child's funeral","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Bezeau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44569642"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:48:49Z","content":"Justine needs to be there for her son's funeral, this is the last time she will see her baby boy... BRING HER HOME!!!!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Monique Goodson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78894206"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:18:24Z","content":"i am a mother and i can not even imagine what Justine is going thru, and she needs to come home be with her family and friends for support through her grieving. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Damaris Morales","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78897612"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:38:46Z","content":"I am a mother of two, she has not been charged with a crime. I would be devastated if I were in her situation. Please let her be freed, she needs to attend her son's funeral","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tami Christofferson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78899896"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:53:58Z","content":"Not particularly important to me but what mother in her sick mind wouldn't want to attend her son's funeral? Losing her son is already hard enough but not being able to attend to his funeral on top of that? That is just insanely stupid.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jaewoo Ahn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/65142865"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:25:11Z","content":"The Canadian government sickens me.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Benjamin Mackenzie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45237634"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:35:51Z","content":"This women has suffered enough grief and should be sent home to be with her family.\r\nPlease have mercy.  Thank you.","like_count"