g mother is being denied the chance to say her final goodbye to her young son, and why? Because our government fails to help Canadians abroad. Shameful! Please help this woman!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michele Kallio","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14585017"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:31:01Z","content":"This is not the first time something like this has happened. This woman should be released to attend her son's funeral and after that before anyone from Canada visits Cuba they should be aware of the rediculos trafic accident detention law that won't allow involved parties to leave the country before the trial","like_count":0,"author_name":"Randy Noel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9207089"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T05:41:11Z","content":"I have a 4 year old, and I cannot imagine the pain that she is going through. She needs to be by her family and friends, not stuck in a foreign country. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lori Urban","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78812782"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:56:13Z","content":"What purpose does the Canadian Embassy serve if not to \"be there\" for Canadians when they are abroad. If you can't do that job, close the embassy, get the hell back home and get to work here and stop wasting taxpayer money.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Diane Hall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38362345"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:58:37Z","content":"Please allow Justine to go home and be with her family and grieve.","like_count":0,"author_name":"elaine derrick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5885198"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:09:58Z","content":"This is probably the hardest and yet most important thing Justine will ever do.  It will affect her for the rest of her life.  Please help.","like_count":0,"author_name":"judith arnold","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26164579"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:35:55Z","content":"My own son has been removed from the U.S. over 8yrs ago! Even though he has