's citizens abroad.\r\nPlease, make this right!","like_count":0,"author_name":"R Doherty","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51522137"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:45:26Z","content":"Canada needs to stand up for there citizens for situations like this!  It is criminal that she is not being released to come home for her son's funeral!  Canadian Government - shame on you!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brenda Dekker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/73410549"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T21:20:30Z","content":"A mother should be present at her child's funeral.  Please help her get back to Canada ASAP.  I recall when I was in Cuba being told by the tour guide that should you get into an accident,   such as hitting a cow roaming freely on the what they call roads, you would be detained and expected to pay thousands of dollars before being released.  This incident with Justine Davis is the reason I will rethink ever travelling back there.  Again please try and help this family.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carole Davis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77146612"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:59:44Z","content":"A mother's love for her child. Help her please.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sharon Janes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43594253"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:35:59Z","content":"I am a mother and I can not imagine ever having to face the loss of a child let alone being denied the right to be at his funeral!  This is beyond sad :(","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sherry Bailey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66274612"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T03:07:14Z","content":"A mother has every right to bury her child and it is disgusting how little the government has done, and we're suppose to put trust in these people... ridiculous. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karen Quan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78801865"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:05:18Z","content":"Il est inconcevable de retenir cette maman et ainsi l'emp\u00ebcher d'assister aux fun\u00e9railles de son enfant.","like_count":0,"author_name":"H\u00e9l\u00e8ne Mercier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61908261"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T01:18:38Z","content":"Justine has to be at her son's funeral.  It is inconceivable that the police are blocking her departure ~ very tragic and heartbreaking.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gail Marion","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74393429"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:13:18Z","content":"She should be allowed to come home at once!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Harlan Stockdale","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/76235932"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:17:24Z","content":"This mother is suffering enough having lost her son.Help her to at least attend his funeral!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rose LeePaget","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78780182"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:25:26Z","content":"Au nom de la dignit\u00e9 et de ce qui est juste.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gisele Poirier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35849816"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:31:46Z","content":"No one should miss their child's funeral","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stephanie Junkin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/77035508"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T14:30:12Z","content":"I have a son and this is a tragedy...Our purpose in life is our children...R.I.P little Angel...my prayers to you Justine to return home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tracey Purdessy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78712744"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T12:36:33Z","content":"It's a tragic event and this mother needs her family and friends for support and she deserves to lay her baby to rest. Let this woman come home now!!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"sheila griffith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78843505"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T16:46:09Z","content":"Because what mother of a three year intentionally causes the accident that killed her baby?! This is mad, she should not have been detained at all, and it would be evil to make her miss her baby's funeral. She has already suffered too much just in losing her child. BRING HER HOME!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cara Fitzell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68811707"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T18:24:55Z","content":"I am a mother who cannot imagine not being at one of children's funeral ","like_count":0,"author_name":"SONYA SMITH","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78870041"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T20:17:38Z","content":"This mother has the right to bury her child, after all it was a very unfortunate accident. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"christine Gooding","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78761299"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T22:25:55Z","content":"I have some personal experience of our government's failure to help citizen's abroad with difficulties.  I have also read about a number of situations similar to this one.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Evelyn Wake","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43270168"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:26:02Z","content":"I am a father, and I can't imagine the pain to suffer through in something like this. Please show compassion, and let her return home.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andreas Zimmermann","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45568303"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T23:32:13Z","content":"Alison Hopper. Have a heart, let her go to the funeral.","like_count":0,"author_name":"alison hopper","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/66041284"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T00:45:27Z","content":"it`s her baby!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"ted hall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78790083"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:33:06Z","content":"WTF....!!!!...I know that my husband and I will NEVER travel to Cuba again and I will tell everyone I know to do the same. This poor woman has suffered ENOUGH!!! LET HER COME HOME NOW!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lois Forsyth","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/62052217"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:48:56Z","content":"Justine has already gone through the most painful heartbreaking thing a parent can go through, losing your child. A part of you dies inside and life as you know it will never again be the same There is not just the sadness and the grief, it is now the hopelessness and helplessness that she is going through trying to get home to say her final good byes, to see his sweet face just one more time, to kiss him and hold his hand just one more time. Any regime who would have anything to do with keeping this woman in custody and putting her through this hell on earth, does not deserve to be called human. It is despicable to think what kind of sick mind is perpetrating this ordeal. The only way Cuba will come out of this according to the rest of the world is to let this woman go home for her child's funeral. The world is watching....","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda McTaggart","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57206021"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:51:44Z","content":"This is a horrible accident and I feel her great loss and pain. Cuba government do not need to add to it. Let he go home!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Antoinette Blanchard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78894494"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T00:57:29Z","content":"I AM A MOTHER AND THIS HITS ME AT MY CORE.  THE LOVE FOR YOUR CHILD DOES NOT EVEN REMOTELY COMPARE TO ANYTHING IN THIS WORLD.  I PRAY AND I CLAIM THAT GOD WILL HAVE HIS HANDS ALL OVER THIS, ALL OVER THE MOTHER'S SPIRIT AND THAT HE TOUCHES THE HEART AND MINDS OF THE CUBAN GOVT. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"KEONDRA RANKIN","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78895087"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:18:33Z","content":"The worst thing any parent can go through is to lose a child.  To be held in a foreign country for no good reason and thus have to miss the funeral and have no chance to say goodbye is unconscionable.  To have your own embassy and government turn their backs and say they can do nothing is inexcusable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"David Lewis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13992188"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:25:25Z","content":"She suffered a great loss, she hasn't been charged with any crime and she derserves to be able to say goodbye to her precious son.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lesia Millette","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78907126"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:52:49Z","content":"Because it is the right thing to do!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joanne Fluke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78911654"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:41:58Z","content":"her only son. gotta give respect ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marlinda Belone","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78921042"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T14:16:58Z","content":"Please allow her to go home...she needs to be with her son one last time ..holding her her is just inhumaine and ignorrant she needs to be there.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Desiree Campbell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78711441"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T14:55:28Z","content":"FOR OBVIOUS REASONS get this woman home.....","like_count":0,"author_name":"angela raymond","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78074283"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:28:47Z","content":"dirty politics can't be more important than human feelings...","like_count":0,"author_name":"berta rosenohl","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16634440"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:33:21Z","content":"sad story...our politicians should put as much pressure as is necessary to bring her home for that sad event.","like_count":0,"author_name":"noa alon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20498421"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:48:30Z","content":"Why is our Canadian a embassy not helping this unfortunate woman?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Margaret King","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/55947661"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T18:27:07Z","content":"Losing a child is an awful experience and the fact that Ca