02-07T01:13:13Z","content":"This is very important for Justine to be allowed to go home to Canada for her son's funeral.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sheila Dashnaw","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78896984"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:23:01Z","content":"I am from Canada, I know what it's like to be stuck in another country & unable to get to your children or help you meet your  child's needs. God Bless Her. I Pray she is able to return home with her child, to put her child at rest. She hasn't been charged with any crime..Let her go home!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debra Mancusi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5653767"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:33:46Z","content":"It is terrible the way the Canadian Government does not get involved  when it's citizens are being unfairly treated by foreign governments. Why is this woman being detained, has their been formal charges brought against her. get it together and find out why she cannot leave to return to Canada. How come we can help other countrys and not look after our own when they need our country's help.Get this woman home where she belongs.","like_count":0,"author_name":"mike clunas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69117004"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T02:48:20Z","content":"No mother should have to miss her own son's funeral!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marysia Pawlak","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78910829"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:11:18Z","content":"The Canadian gov't. too often fails to support it's citizens outside of Canada, and I am sick of their non responsive, or at best, wimpy behaviour in many difficult situations that travellers may find themselves in. How can Canadians have any confidence in their gov't. or it's diplomatic agents when we see this failure to act far too often? This case should not be ignored or allowed to drag on-these people are suffering enough, as it is. Show some strength and compassion, for a change.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Faye Christopher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/74179111"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T13:11:16Z","content":"To get Justine Davis home where she belongs. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jenna-Rae Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78705327"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T13:51:14Z","content":"This is Justine's child for God sakes!!! I think this is plain mental abuse to deprive her from being there. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kim Neville","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15415941"},{"created_at":"2014-02-07T03:44:07Z","content":"We have travelled to and in Cuba  for 30 years and know how little one can expect from the Authorities .  However this is\r\nNot an issue of illegal departure\r\nOr other significant political restriction - it will reflect very very poorly on Cuba who depends on\r\nTourism, especially from Canada.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karin and Hugh Taylor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51475419"},{"created_at":"2014-02-05T14:51:39Z","content":"We should ban travel to Cuba until all Canadians in similar surcomstances are released and we have agreements in place to quick release other Canadians in the future. Perhaps a few hundred million dollars less coming into their country for a time will open up their minds and hearts to sympathetic reason.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Neil Hussey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/78714987"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T14:18:13Z","content":"No parent should have to bury their child!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tina Morgan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27132096"},{"created_at":"2014-02-06T15:00:21Z","content":"That poor woman.","like_count":0,"author_name":"James Bacque","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29469359"}]}